:Namespace Aux
(вҺ•IO вҺ•ML вҺ•WX)вҶҗ1 1 3

вҲҮ DepositData data
     
     вҚқвҲҮ make sure the data is a vector of vectors
     
 :If 2=вҚҙвҚҙdata вӢ„ dataвҶҗвҶ“[1]data вӢ„ :EndIf
 ##.Aux.dataвҶҗdata
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ DepositNames names
     
 ##.Aux.var_namesвҶҗnames
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ dataвҶҗGetData n
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  need some mechanism for keeping variable names
 :If 0вү вҺ•NC'##.Aux.data'
     dataвҶҗnвҶ‘##.Aux.data
 :Else
     dataвҶҗвҚ¬
 :EndIf
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ Plot_xy(i j);c;r;n;names;vars;x;y
     
 x yвҶҗ##.Aux.data[i j]
 cвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndDP ##.Dutils.Corr ##.Aux.data[i j]
 rвҶҗ?10000
 nвҶҗ'p',вҚ•r
 namesвҶҗ##.Aux.VarNamesвүў##.Aux.data
 varsвҶҗnames[i j]
     
 n #.grf.вҲҶQP ##.Aux.data[i j]
 n #.grf.вҲҶQT vars,(вҠӮ'Correlation: ',вҚ•c)
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ Plot_xy_by_Name(nx ny);c;r;n;names;vars;x;y;i;j
     
 namesвҶҗ##.Aux.VarNamesвүў##.Aux.data
 i jвҶҗnamesвҚіnx ny
 x yвҶҗ##.Aux.data[i j]
 cвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndDP ##.Dutils.Corr ##.Aux.data[i j]
 rвҶҗ?10000
 nвҶҗ'p',вҚ•r
 varsвҶҗnames[i j]
     
 n #.grf.вҲҶQP ##.Aux.data[i j]
 n #.grf.вҲҶQT vars,(вҠӮ'Correlation: ',вҚ•c)
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ namesвҶҗVarNames n
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  need some mechanism for keeping variable names
 :If 0вү вҺ•NC'##.Stats.Aux.var_names'
     namesвҶҗnвҶ‘##.Aux.var_names
 :Else
     namesвҶҗ'x',ВЁвҚ•ВЁвҚіn
 :EndIf
     
 :Return
