(вҺ•IO вҺ•ML вҺ•WX)вҶҗ1 1 3



вҲҮ QвҶҗChiSq_A(Xs dof);ker;hd;mult;int;To
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  the right tail area for a critical ChiSq and dof
     
 :If Xs<0.01
     QвҶҗ1-ChiSq_P Xs dof
     :Return
 :EndIf
     
     вҚқвҲҮ 26.4.2
 dofвҢҠвҶҗ300
 ToвҶҗ{(Г—вҚә-вҚө)Г—вҚә+(Г—вҚө-вҚә)Г—вҚі1+|вҚө-вҚә}
 kerвҶҗ{(вҚө*hd-1)Г—*-вҚөГ·2}
 hdвҶҗdofГ·2
 multвҶҗГ·(2*hd)Г—!hd-1
     
 intвҶҗ(ker ##.Dutils.вҲҶGQ)##.Dutils.вҲҶQUAD Xs 250 50
 QвҶҗmultГ—int
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ NвҶҗChiSq_Da(ChiSq alpha);Fun;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  s вҶҗ ChiSq_Da ChiSq Alpha -- Critical degrees-of-freedom for ChiSquare
     вҚқвҲҮ                    alpha is the right "tail" area  cumdf вүЎ p = 1-alpha
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 FunвҶҗ{alpha-##.Distrib.ChiSq_Q ChiSq вҚө}
 NвҶҗвҢҲFun ##.Dutils.HalfStepI 1 170 24
 NвҶҗNвҢҠ1000000
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ NвҶҗChiSq_Dp(ChiSq cumdf);Fun;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  s вҶҗ ChiSq_Da ChiSq p -- Critical degrees-of-freedom for ChiSquare
     вҚқвҲҮ                      cumdf вүЎ p = 1-alpha
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 FunвҶҗ{cumdf-##.Distrib.ChiSq_P ChiSq вҚө}
 NвҶҗвҢҲFun ##.Dutils.HalfStepI 1 170 24
 NвҶҗNвҢҠ1000000
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ QвҶҗChiSq_P(Xs dof);ker;hd;mult;int;To;NOP;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  Given:   Critical ChiSquare and degrees of freedom
     вҚқвҲҮ  Return:  the cumulatgive probability (integral from the left).
     вҚқвҲҮ     A&S 26.4.2
     
 dofвҢҠвҶҗ300
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 ToвҶҗ{(Г—вҚә-вҚө)Г—вҚә+(Г—вҚө-вҚә)Г—вҚі1+|вҚө-вҚә}
 kerвҶҗ{(вҚө*hd-1)Г—*-вҚөГ·2}
 hdвҶҗdofГ·2
 multвҶҗГ·(2*hd)Г—!hd-1
 NOPвҶҗ50                                      вҚқ adequate no. of panels for most computations
 :If (dof=1)вҲ§(Xs<0.4) вӢ„ NOPвҶҗ500 вӢ„ :EndIf      вҚқ tighten up :: silly part of the chi-square space
 :If (dof=1)вҲ§(Xs<0.01) вӢ„ NOPвҶҗ5000 вӢ„ :EndIf
     
 intвҶҗ(ker ##.Dutils.вҲҶGQ)##.Dutils.вҲҶQUAD 0 Xs NOP
 QвҶҗmultГ—int
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ QвҶҗChiSq_Q(Xs dof);ker;hd;mult;int;To
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  the right tail area for a critical ChiSq and dof
     
 :If Xs<0.01
     QвҶҗ1-ChiSq_P Xs dof
     :Return
 :EndIf
     
     вҚқвҲҮ 26.4.2
 dofвҢҠвҶҗ300
 ToвҶҗ{(Г—вҚә-вҚө)Г—вҚә+(Г—вҚө-вҚә)Г—вҚі1+|вҚө-вҚә}
 kerвҶҗ{(вҚө*hd-1)Г—*-вҚөГ·2}
 hdвҶҗdofГ·2
 multвҶҗГ·(2*hd)Г—!hd-1
     
 intвҶҗ(ker ##.Dutils.вҲҶGQ)##.Dutils.вҲҶQUAD Xs 250 50
 QвҶҗmultГ—int
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ resвҶҗChiSq_XAD xad;k;X;alpha;dof;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
      вҚқвҲҮ return the missing element given the other 2 out of: ChiSq  alpha  dof
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 kвҶҗвҠғвҚёxadвүЎВЁвҠӮвҚ¬
 X alpha dofвҶҗxad
     
 :Select k
 :Case 1                               вҚқ  get X == ChiSquare
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.ChiSq_Xa alpha dof
 :Case 2                                вҚқ  get alpha
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.ChiSq_Q X dof
 :Case 3                                вҚқ  get degrees-of-freedom
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.ChiSq_Da X alpha
 :EndSelect
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ resвҶҗChiSq_XPD xad;k;X;dof;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;cumdf
     
      вҚқвҲҮ return the missing element given the other 2 out of: ChiSq  cumdf  dof
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 kвҶҗвҠғвҚёxadвүЎВЁвҠӮвҚ¬
 X cumdf dofвҶҗxad
     
 :Select k
 :Case 1                               вҚқ  get X == ChiSquare
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.ChiSq_Xp cumdf dof
 :Case 2                                вҚқ  get alpha
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.ChiSq_Q X dof
 :Case 3                                вҚқ  get degrees-of-freedom
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.ChiSq_Dp X cumdf
 :EndSelect
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ xsвҶҗChiSq_Xa(alpha dof);Funx;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;y130;y140;y150;c
     
     вҚқвҲҮ Given:   alpha (right-hand tail) and degress of freedom
     вҚқвҲҮ Return:  the critical value of ChiSquare
     вҚқвҲҮ Based on alpha  A&S 26.4.2
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
     вҚқ dofвҢҠвҶҗ150
 :If dofвүӨ150
     :If (dof=1)вҲ§(alpha>0.9999) вӢ„ xsвҶҗ0 вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf              вҚқ  at .9999 xs~1EВҜ7  and I can't compute anything higher
     FunxвҶҗ{alpha-##.Distrib.ChiSq_Q вҚө dof}
     :If (dof=1)вҲ§(alpha>0.75)
         FunxвҶҗ{(1-alpha)-##.Distrib.ChiSq_P вҚө dof}                вҚқ  P is more accurate than Q for dof=1  at very low P or big Q (alpha)
     :EndIf
     вҚқ alpha,FunxВЁ1EВҜ9 300
     xsвҶҗFunx ##.Dutils.HalfStep 1EВҜ9 250 30
 :Else
     вҚқ  for large dof, A&S 26.4.16  didn't work as I coded it.  Maybe I misunderstood something.
     вҚқ  but quadratically extapolating in log log space the values for dof = 130 140 and 150
     вҚқ  seems to have modest error for dof<600.  Sensible answers up to 100,000;  a million isn't so good!!!
     вҚқ  I used two sanity checks:  as you go down in alpha, the ChiSq should be close to dof at вҚә=.5; and
     вҚқ  the ChiSq should monotonically increase.  Over 700 they hold except for very wee вҚәs: .0005 and .0001
     y130вҶҗChiSq_Xa alpha 130
     y140вҶҗChiSq_Xa alpha 140
     y150вҶҗChiSq_Xa alpha 150
     cвҶҗ(10вҚҹy130 y140 y150)вҢ№(10вҚҹ130 140 150)вҲҳ.*0 1 2
     xsвҶҗ10*c+.Г—(10вҚҹdof)вҲҳ.*0 1 2
 :EndIf
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ xsвҶҗChiSq_Xp(cumdf dof);Funx;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;y130;y140;y150;c
     
     вҚқвҲҮ Given:   cumdf (left-hand tail) and degress of freedom
     вҚқвҲҮ Return:  the critical value of ChiSquare
     вҚқвҲҮ Based on alpha  A&S 26.4.2
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
     вҚқ dofвҢҠвҶҗ150
 :If dofвүӨ150
     :If (dof=1)вҲ§(cumdf<0.0001) вӢ„ xsвҶҗ0 вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf              вҚқ  at .9999 xs~1EВҜ7  and I can't compute anything higher
     FunxвҶҗ{cumdf-##.Distrib.ChiSq_P вҚө dof}
     :If (dof=1)вҲ§(cumdf<0.25)
         FunxвҶҗ{(1-cumdf)-##.Distrib.ChiSq_Q вҚө dof}                вҚқ  P is more accurate than Q for dof=1  at very low P or big Q (alpha)
     :EndIf
     вҚқ alpha,FunxВЁ1EВҜ9 300
     xsвҶҗFunx ##.Dutils.HalfStep 1EВҜ9 250 30
 :Else
     вҚқ  for large dof, A&S 26.4.16  didn't work as I coded it.  Maybe I misunderstood something.
     вҚқ  but quadratically extapolating in log log space the values for dof = 130 140 and 150
     вҚқ  seems to have modest error for dof<600.  Sensible answers up to 100,000;  a million isn't so good!!!
     вҚқ  I used two sanity checks:  as you go down in alpha, the ChiSq should be close to dof at вҚә=.5; and
     вҚқ  the ChiSq should monotonically increase.  Over 700 they hold except for very wee вҚәs: .0005 and .0001
     y130вҶҗChiSq_Xa alpha 130
     y140вҶҗChiSq_Xa alpha 140
     y150вҶҗChiSq_Xa alpha 150
     cвҶҗ(10вҚҹy130 y140 y150)вҢ№(10вҚҹ130 140 150)вҲҳ.*0 1 2
     xsвҶҗ10*c+.Г—(10вҚҹdof)вҲҳ.*0 1 2
 :EndIf
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ QвҶҗChiSq_alpha(Xs dof);ker;hd;mult;int;To
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  the right tail area for a critical ChiSq and dof
     
 :If Xs<0.01
     QвҶҗ1-##.Distrib.ChiSq_P Xs dof
     :Return
 :EndIf
     
     вҚқвҲҮ 26.4.2
 ToвҶҗ{(Г—вҚә-вҚө)Г—вҚә+(Г—вҚө-вҚә)Г—вҚі1+|вҚө-вҚә}
 kerвҶҗ{(вҚө*hd-1)Г—*-вҚөГ·2}
 hdвҶҗdofГ·2
 multвҶҗГ·(2*hd)Г—!hd-1
     
 intвҶҗ(ker ##.Dutils.вҲҶGQ)##.Dutils.вҲҶQUAD Xs 1000 50
 QвҶҗmultГ—int
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ pвҶҗFratio_A(F dn dd);x;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   Given:   a Critical_Fratio value, the numerator and denominator degress of freedom
     вҚқвҲҮ   Return:  the tail area - alpha
     вҚқвҲҮ
     вҚқвҲҮ   A&S  26.6.2  p946     :: in A&S this is "Q"  (1-P)
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 xвҶҗddГ·dd+FГ—dn
 pвҶҗ##.Dutils.IncBetaI x,0.5Г—dd dn    вҚқ  integrals for dofd 1 and 2 take a while
                                            вҚқ  and as written only good to 2 or 3 digits
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ NвҶҗFratio_Da(F alpha dofn);Fun;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  Return: Critical denominator-degrees-of-freedom for the F-ratio cumlulative distribution
     вҚқвҲҮ  Given:  Critical Fratio value, alpha (tail probability), and   numerator-degrees-of-freedom.
     вҚқвҲҮ
     вҚқвҲҮ                    alpha is the "tail" area  alpha = 1-p (the cumulatlive
     вҚқвҲҮ                    distribution)
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 FunвҶҗ{alpha-##.Distrib.Fratio_alpha F dofn вҚө}
 NвҶҗвҢҲFun ##.Dutils.HalfStepI 1 100000 24
 NвҶҗNвҢҠ1000000
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ NвҶҗFratio_Dp(F cumdf dofn);Fun;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;alpha
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  Return: Critical denominator-degrees-of-freedom for the F-ratio cumlulative distribution
     вҚқвҲҮ  Given:  Critical Fratio value, alpha (tail probability), and   numerator-degrees-of-freedom.
     вҚқвҲҮ
     вҚқвҲҮ                    alpha is the "tail" area  alpha = 1-p (the cumulatlive
     вҚқвҲҮ                    distribution)
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 alphaвҶҗ1-cumdf
 FunвҶҗ{alpha-##.Distrib.Fratio_alpha F dofn вҚө}
 NвҶҗвҢҲFun ##.Dutils.HalfStepI 1 100000 24
 NвҶҗNвҢҠ1000000
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ resвҶҗFratio_FAND fand;k;F;alpha;dofn;dofd;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
      вҚқвҲҮ return the missing element given the other 3 out of: F  alpha  dofn  dofd
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 kвҶҗвҚёfandвүЎВЁвҠӮвҚ¬
 F alpha dofn dofdвҶҗfand
     
 :Select k
 :Case 1                               вҚқ  get F
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.Fratio_Fa alpha dofn dofd
 :Case 2                                вҚқ  get alpha
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.Fratio_A F dofn dofd
 :Case 3                                вҚқ  get numerator-degrees-of-freedom
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.Fratio_Na F alpha dofd
 :Case 4                                вҚқ  get denominator-degrees-of-freedom
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.Fratio_Da F alpha dofn
 :EndSelect
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ resвҶҗFratio_FPND fand;k;F;cumdf;dofn;dofd;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
      вҚқвҲҮ return the missing element given the other 3 out of: F  cumdf  dofn  dofd
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 kвҶҗвҚёfandвүЎВЁвҠӮвҚ¬
 F cumdf dofn dofdвҶҗfand
     
 :Select k
 :Case 1                               вҚқ  get F
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.Fratio_Fp cumdf dofn dofd
 :Case 2                                вҚқ  get alpha
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.Fratio_P F dofn dofd
 :Case 3                                вҚқ  get numerator-degrees-of-freedom
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.Fratio_Np F cumdf dofd
 :Case 4                                вҚқ  get denominator-degrees-of-freedom
     resвҶҗ##.Distrib.Fratio_Dp F cumdf dofn
 :EndSelect
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ FвҶҗFratio_Fa and;alpha;dofn;dofd;Funx;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ deliver the critical F-ratio for given alpha and numerator and
     вҚқвҲҮ         denominator degrees of freedom.
     вҚқвҲҮ  accurate for dofd=1 to just 2-3 digits (takes way toooo long
     вҚқвҲҮ     to get more accuracy:  change the NON in IncBetaI to 100000
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 alpha dofn dofdвҶҗ3вҶ‘and,1,1
     вҚқ  search for the F delivers the given alpha
     вҚқ  create the search function
     вҚқ FunxвҶҗ{alpha-Fratio_alpha вҚө dofn dofd}
 FunxвҶҗ{alpha-Fratio_Q вҚө dofn dofd}
     
 FвҶҗFunx ##.Dutils.HalfStep 0.1(1+2*20)50
 FвҶҗ10000000000вҢҠF
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ FвҶҗFratio_Fp and;cumdf;alpha;dofn;dofd;Funx;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ deliver the critical F-ratio for given alpha and numerator and
     вҚқвҲҮ         denominator degrees of freedom.
     вҚқвҲҮ  accurate for dofd=1 to just 2-3 digits (takes way toooo long
     вҚқвҲҮ     to get more accuracy:  change the NON in IncBetaI to 100000
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 cumdf dofn dofdвҶҗ3вҶ‘and,1,1
 alphaвҶҗ1-cumdf
     вҚқ  search for the F delivers the given alpha
     вҚқ  create the search function
     вҚқ FunxвҶҗ{alpha-Fratio_alpha вҚө dofn dofd}
 FunxвҶҗ{alpha-Fratio_Q вҚө dofn dofd}
 FвҶҗFunx ##.Dutils.HalfStep 0.1(1+2*20)50
 FвҶҗ10000000000вҢҠF
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ NвҶҗFratio_Na(F alpha dofd);Fun;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  Return: Critical numerator-degrees-of-freedom for the F-ratio cumlulative distribution
     вҚқвҲҮ  Given:  Critical Fratio value, alpha (tail integral), and denominator-degrees-of-freedom.
     вҚқвҲҮ                    alpha is the "tail" area  alpha = 1-p (the cumulatlive
     вҚқвҲҮ                    distribution)
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 FunвҶҗ{alpha-Fratio_Q F вҚө dofd}
 NвҶҗвҢҲFun ##.Dutils.HalfStepI 1 1000 24
