вҲҮ PвҶҗFratio_P(F dn dd);x;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   Given:   a Critical_Fratio value, the numerator and denominator degress of freedom
     вҚқвҲҮ   Return:  cumulative probability (area from -infinity to F)
     вҚқвҲҮ   A&S  26.6.2  p946
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 xвҶҗddГ·dd+FГ—dn
 PвҶҗ1-##.Dutils.IncBetaI x,0.5Г—dd dn
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ pвҶҗFratio_Q(F dn dd);x;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   Given:   a Critical_Fratio value, the numerator and denominator degress of freedom
     вҚқвҲҮ   Return:  the tail area - alpha
     вҚқвҲҮ
     вҚқвҲҮ   A&S  26.6.2  p946     :: in A&S this is "Q"  (1-P)
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 xвҶҗddГ·dd+FГ—dn
 pвҶҗ##.Dutils.IncBetaI x,0.5Г—dd dn    вҚқ  integrals for dofd 1 and 2 take a while
                                            вҚқ  and as written only good to 2 or 3 digits
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ zвҶҗNormal_A x;ker;f;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  z вҶҗ Normal x --  the statisticians error fcn:  cum. normal prob. dist.
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 kerвҶҗ{*-0.5Г—вҚө*2}
 fвҶҗГ·0.5*вҚЁв—Ӣ2
     
 :If xвүӨВҜ4.06
     zвҶҗ1-fГ—ker ##.Dutils.вҲҶGQ ##.Dutils.вҲҶQUAD ВҜ50 x 100
 :ElseIf x<0
     zвҶҗ0.5+fГ—ker ##.Dutils.вҲҶGQ ##.Dutils.вҲҶQUAD 0(|x)100
 :ElseIf xвүӨ4.06
     zвҶҗ0.5-fГ—ker ##.Dutils.вҲҶGQ ##.Dutils.вҲҶQUAD 0 x 100
 :Else
     zвҶҗfГ—ker ##.Dutils.вҲҶGQ ##.Dutils.вҲҶQUAD x 50 100
 :EndIf
     
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ zвҶҗNormal_P x;ker;f;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
