вҲҮ dofвҶҗStudent_Da(t alpha);Fun;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  dof вҶҗ Student_D (t alpha)  -- degrees needed to get a t at the given alpha
     вҚқвҲҮ                    alpha is the "tail" area  alpha = 1-p (the cumulatlive
     вҚқвҲҮ                    distribution )
     
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 FunвҶҗ{(1-alpha)-##.Distrib.Student_P t вҚө}
