вҲҮ cвҶҗCorr(x y);ax;ay;dx;dy;sosx;sosy;soxy;srx;sry
     
 ax ayвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwosВЁx y)Г·вүўx
 dx dyвҶҗx y-ax ay
 sosx sosyвҶҗ##.Dutils.SumByTwosВЁ(dx*2)(dy*2)
 srx sryвҶҗsosx sosy*0.5
 soxyвҶҗ##.Dutils.SumByTwos dxГ—dy
 cвҶҗsoxyГ·srxГ—sry
     
 :Return
