вҲҮ (a d e z)вҶҗImplicitQL(v a d e n);l;j;m;p;eps;g;r;s;c;i;f;b;ia;To
     
     вҚқвҲҮ      AвҶҗQL where Q is orthagonal and L is lower triangular
     вҚқвҲҮ      plinked from GLIB:EIGPAK
     вҚқвҲҶ      FROM NUMERISCHE MATHEMATIK 12, 337-383 (1968)
     
 ToвҶҗ{(Г—вҚә-вҚө)+вҚә+(Г—вҚө-вҚә)Г—вҚі1+|вҚө-вҚә}
 epsвҶҗ16*ВҜ13
 eвҶҗ1вҢҪe
 iaвҶҗвҚіn
 jвҶҗ0
 :For l :In вҚіn-1
TryAgain:
     mвҶҗ(l-1)вҶ“вҚіn-1
     mвҶҗ(l-1)+((|e[m])вүӨepsГ—((|d[m])+|d[m+1]))вҚі1
     pвҶҗd[l]
     :If m=l вӢ„ jвҶҗ0 вӢ„ :Continue вӢ„ :EndIf
     j+вҶҗ1
     :If 30<j вӢ„ 'Routine has failed.  Returns Eigenvalues found so far.' вӢ„ l-вҶҗ2 вӢ„ :Leave вӢ„ :EndIf
     rвҶҗ4в—ӢgвҶҗ(d[l+1]-p)Г·2Г—e[l]
     gвҶҗd[m]+(e[l]Г·g+rГ—1-2Г—g<0)-p
     sвҶҗcвҶҗ1
     pвҶҗd[m]
     iвҶҗm
     :For i :In (m-1)To l
         fвҶҗsГ—e[i]
         bвҶҗcГ—e[i]
         :If </|f g
             e[i+1]вҶҗgГ—rвҶҗ4в—ӢcвҶҗfГ·g
             sвҶҗcГ·r
             cвҶҗГ·r
     вҚқ                'gb'##.Dutils.Watcher i l j g s c f b(e[i+1])
     
         :Else
             e[i+1]вҶҗfГ—rвҶҗ4в—ӢcвҶҗgГ·f
             cвҶҗcГ—sвҶҗГ·r
     вҚқ                'gs'##.Dutils.Watcher i l j g s c f b(e[i+1])
     
         :EndIf
         rвҶҗd[i]+p
         pвҶҗ(cГ—fвҶҗ(cГ—d[i])-sГ—b)-sГ—gвҶҗ(cГ—b)-sГ—p
         gвҶҗ(sГ—f)+cГ—g
         d[i+1]вҶҗr-p
         :If v
             a[ia;i+0 1]вҶҗa[ia;i+0 1]+.Г—2 2вҚҙc,s,(-s),c
         :EndIf
     вҚқ           'el'##.Dutils.Watcher i l j g s c f b r p(e[i])(d[i+1])
     
     :EndFor  вҚқ on i
     d[l]вҶҗp
     e[l]вҶҗg
     e[m]вҶҗ0
     :GoTo TryAgain
 :EndFor
     
 zвҶҗ(l+1)вҶ‘d
 aвҶҗ((l+1),n)вҶ‘a
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ ixвҶҗIncBetaI(x nu1 nu2);ker;NON;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
      вҚқвҲҮ Incomplete Beta Function  A&S p944  26.5.1
      вҚқвҲҮ Given:    the abscissa, and two degrees of freedom
     
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 kerвҶҗ{вҚө=0:0 вӢ„ (вҚө*nu1-1)Г—(1-вҚө)*nu2-1}
 NONвҶҗ100
 :If (nu2вүӨ4)вҲ§(nu1вүӨ1) вӢ„ NONвҶҗ1000 вӢ„ :EndIf
     вҚқ :If (nu2<2)вҲ§(nu1<1) вӢ„ NONвҶҗ200000 вӢ„ :EndIf
     
 ixвҶҗ(Г·##.Dutils.Beta nu1 nu2)Г—(ker ##.Dutils.вҲҶGQ)##.Dutils.вҲҶQUAD 0 x NON
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ ibвҶҗIncBeta_Integers(x nu1 nu2);omx;mult;sum;To;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ A&S 26.5.7  p944
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 ToвҶҗ{(Г—вҚә-вҚө)Г—вҚә+(Г—вҚө-вҚә)Г—вҚі1+|вҚө-вҚә}
 omxвҶҗ1-x
 multвҶҗ(omx*nu1+nu2-1)
 sumвҶҗ+/{(вҚө!nu1+nu2-1)Г—(xГ·omx)*вҚө}ВЁ0 To nu1-1
     
 ibвҶҗ1-multГ—sum
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ cpвҶҗMakeChebychevPolynomialX(order nd)
     
     вҚқвҲҮ Create a chebychev polylnomial "x" vector
     вҚқвҲҮ order defaults to nd if order=0
     
 orderвҶҗ(|orderГ—orderвү 0)+(ndГ—order=0)
 cpвҶҗndвҚҙвҢҪ2в—Ӣ((в—Ӣ1)Г—ВҜ1+2Г—вҚіorder)Г·orderГ—2
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ cpвҶҗMakeChebychevPolys(x order);i
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   Create a bunch of chebychev polylnomials recursively; given x and order
     вҚқвҲҮ   The first two columns are 1 and x;  therefore, there will be order+1 columns
 cpвҶҗ1,[1.5]x
 :For i :In 2вҶ“вҚіorder+1
     cp,вҶҗ(2Г—xГ—cp[;i-1])-cp[;i-2]
 :EndFor
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ (fx co)вҶҗMakeForsythePolys(x order);вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;on;n;zo;ave;zi;zossum;zissum;gam;del;zn
     
      вҚқвҲҮ make forsythe polynomials (recursively) based on X and of hightest power: order
      вҚқвҲҮ    that will be order+1 columns as the firat column will be 1s.
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗвҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 onвҶҗ1+order
 nвҶҗвүўx
     
     вҚқ                   f  will be the model with order+1 variables (columns)
     вҚқ                   f1 will be ones
     вҚқ                   f2 will be the 1st Forsythe Polynomial:  x-xave
     вҚқ                   fn will be the (n-1)th order Forsythe polynomial
     
 zoвҶҗnвҚҙ1
 aveвҶҗ##.Dutils.Average x
 ziвҶҗx-ave
     
 fxвҶҗzo,[1.5]zi
 coвҶҗ1 2вҚҙave 0
 :For i :In 2вҶ“вҚіon
     zossumвҶҗ##.Dutils.SumByTwos zo*2
     zissumвҶҗ##.Dutils.SumByTwos zi*2
     gamвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwos xГ—zi*2)Г·zissum
     delвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwos xГ—ziГ—zo)Г·zossum
     znвҶҗ(ziГ—x-gam)-delГ—zo
     zoвҶҗzi
     ziвҶҗzn
     fx,вҶҗzn
     coвҚӘвҶҗgam del
 :EndFor
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ MakeReadMe;rn;rm
     
 rnвҶҗвҶ“1 1вҶ“вҺ•CR'##.Dutils.Notes'
 rnвҶҗ##.Dutils.RtbВЁrn
 rmвҶҗ(вҠӮ'rm,вҶҗвҠӮ'''),ВЁrn,ВЁ''''
 rmвҶҗ'{rm}вҶҗReadMe' '  '('rmвҶҗ''''')('rm,вҶҗвҠӮ''      generated by ##.Dutils.MakeReadMe    using   ##.Dutils.Notes'''),rm
 вҺ•CS'#'
 вҺ•FX rm
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ nвҶҗMatNormFrob m
 nвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwos,m*2)*0.5
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ nвҶҗMatNormInf m
 nвҶҗвҠғвҢҲ/##.Dutils.SumByTwosВЁвҶ“m
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ nвҶҗMatNormOne m
 nвҶҗвҠғвҢҲ/##.Dutils.SumByTwosВЁвҶ“[1]m
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ zвҶҗNormal x
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  z вҶҗ Normal x --  ordinate of the normal distribution
     
 zвҶҗ(*-0.5Г—x*2)Г·(в—Ӣ2)*0.5
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ ntabвҶҗNormalTableOrder tab;вҺ•IO;r;c;n;w;m;k;вҺ•ML
     
     вҚқвҲҮ     put the output anova table into normal format:
     вҚқвҲҮ         A B AB   C AC BC ABC  D AD .....
     вҚқвҲҮ     instead of the straight format it was created in:
     вҚқвҲҮ         A B C D ....  AB AC AD..BC BD ....  ABC ABD .....
     
 вҺ•IOвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•MLвҶҗ1
     
 r cвҶҗвҚҙtab
 nвҶҗвҢҠ2вҚҹ(1.5+r)
     
 wвҶҗCompleteComb n
 mвҶҗвҚҙw
 kвҶҗвҚӢвҶ‘(вҢҲ/вҚҙВЁw)вҶ‘ВЁвҢҪВЁw
     
     вҚқ   SHOW 'X' X
     вҚқ   SHOW 'M' M
     вҚқ   SHOW 'W' W
     вҚқ   SHOW 'R C N' R C N
     вҚқ   SHOW 'Y' Y
     
 ntabвҶҗtab[k;]
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ Notes
     вҚқ================================================================================
     вҚқ
     вҚқ   The basic data structure is a vector of equi-length vectors.
     вҚқ     Generally arguments to the statistical routines are selections
     вҚқ     from this set of vectors or a ravel (вҠғ,/...) of a set of them.
     вҚқ
     вҚқ================================================================================
     вҚқ
     вҚқ   ##.Aux:        (pretty much for how Koko would use this code)
     вҚқ     built to facillitate various calls to functions on a set of data
     вҚқ     has functions to deposit and retrieve the data:
     вҚқ              ##.Aux.DepositData  data    вҚқ  it will split {вҶ“[1]вҚө} a matrix
     вҚқ         dataвҶҗ##.Aux.GetData
     вҚқ     has funcltions to deposit and retrieve variable names
     вҚқ              ##.Aux.DepositNames  names
     вҚқ        namesвҶҗ##.Aux.VarNames
     вҚқ     has two diddly plotting functions:
     вҚқ              ##.Aux.Plot_xy i j   вҚқ  i j are indexes into data
     вҚқ              ##.Aux.Plot_xy_by_Name namei namej  вҚқ  names in VarNames
     вҚқ
     вҚқ================================================================================
     вҚқ
     вҚқ   ##.Stats:
     вҚқ     contains statistical functions that take data vectors as arguments
     вҚқ     if the function has more than one logical output, the results are returned
     вҚқ     in a  {shy} namespace.  If just one, it is returned {shy}.
     вҚқ              {ns} вҶҗ Anova v  levels  norm
     вҚқ              {ns} вҶҗ AnovaPool nb ms lev alpha
     вҚқ              {ns} вҶҗ Pcomps vov
     вҚқ              {ns} вҶҗ RegressMultipleLinear  yv  xvov
     вҚқ              {ns} вҶҗ RegressPolynmomial     yv  xv   order
     вҚқ              {ns} вҶҗ RegressFosythe         yv  xv   order
     вҚқ              {ns} вҶҗ RegressChebychev       yv  xv   order
     вҚқ
     вҚқ           Xans Dl вҶҗ SimutaneousEquations   Amat Rvector
     вҚқ
     вҚқ              {cm} вҶҗ Correl vov
     вҚқ              {ac} вҶҗ AutoCorr v
     вҚқ              {cc} вҶҗ CrossCorr v_stationary v_moving_forward
     вҚқ              {ns) вҶҗ CrossTabs v1 v2
     вҚқ              {ns} вҶҗ FourierTransform v
     вҚқ
     вҚқ================================================================================
     вҚқ
     вҚқ   ##.Distrib:
     вҚқ     contains the various distribution functions:  P (or p) is cumdf (left int.)
     вҚқ                                                   Aux right tail :: Q in A&S
     вҚқ                                                   D is degrees of freedom
     вҚқ
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Normal_y x             вҚқ  the distribution ordinate at x
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Normal_Xa alpha        вҚқ  x given alpha (right-tail integral)
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Normal_Xp cumdf        вҚқ  x given p or cumdf (left integral)
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Normal_P x             вҚқ  cumdf (p) at x
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Normal_A x             вҚқ  alpha (right tail) at x
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Normal_Q x             вҚқ  alpha (right tail) at x
     вҚқ
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Student_Ta alpha dof   вҚқ  Critical t given вҚә and dof
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Student_Tp cumdf dof   вҚқ  Critical t given p and dof
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Student_P t            вҚқ  cumdf (p) at t and dof
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Student_A t            вҚқ  alpha (right tail) at t and dof
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Student_Q t            вҚқ  alpha (right tail) at t and dof
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Student_Da t alpha     вҚқ  degrees of freedom needed for t,вҚә
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Student_Dp t cumdf     вҚқ  degrees of freedom needed for t,p
     вҚқ
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ ChiSq_Xa alpha dof     вҚқ  critical ChiSq given A and dof
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ ChiSq_Xp cumdf dof     вҚқ  critical ChiSq given p and dof
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ ChiSq_P  ChiSq dof     вҚқ  cumdf at that ChiSq
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ ChiSq_A  ChiSq dof     вҚқ  right tail (alpha) for that ChiSq
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ ChiSq_Q  ChiSq dof     вҚқ  right tail for that ChiSq
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ ChiSq_Da ChiSq alpha   вҚқ  degrees-of-freedom for ChiSQ & alpha
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ ChiSq_Dp ChiSq alpha   вҚқ  degrees-of-freedom for ChiSQ & cumdf
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ ChiSQ_XAD  X вҚә dodf    вҚқ  delivers whichever arg. is вҚ¬
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ ChiSQ_XPD  X p dodf    вҚқ  delivers whichever arg. is вҚ¬
     вҚқ
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Fratio_Fp cumdf dn dd  вҚқ  Crit_F for p dof_num dof_denom
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Fratio_Fa alpha dn dd  вҚқ  Crit_F for вҚә dof_num dof_denom
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Fratio_P  Fcrit dn dd  вҚқ  cumdf  for F dofn dofd
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Fratio_A  Fcrit dn dd  вҚқ  alpha  for F dofn dofd
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Fratio_Q  Fcrit dn dd  вҚқ  alpha  for F dofn dofd
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Fratio_Np F p dd       вҚқ  numerator dof
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Fratio_Na F вҚә dd       вҚқ  numerator dof
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Fratio_Dp F p dd       вҚқ  denominator dof
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Fratio_Da F вҚә dd       вҚқ  denominator dof
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Fratio_FPND F p dn dd  вҚқ  delivers whichever arg. is вҚ¬
     вҚқ              r вҶҗ Fratio_FAND F вҚә dn dd  вҚқ  delivers whichever arg. is вҚ¬
     вҚқ
     вҚқ================================================================================
     вҚқ
     вҚқ   ##.Dutils:
     вҚқ     contains utilities used by any routines
     вҚқ     ALL pathing to these functions is explicit; as well as any other fcns.
     вҚқ
     вҚқ================================================================================
     вҚқ
     вҚқ   ##.Stuff:
     вҚқ     contains functions that were used to test the working functions and hold
     вҚқ      or make data to do so.
     вҚқ      Doit_...  will run an example; some compare with MOST
     вҚқ              Doit_Anova
     вҚқ              Doit_Pcomps
     вҚқ              Doit_Regress
     вҚқ      Test_...  reproduces parts of tables that can be found in A&S or texts.
     вҚқ              Test_Student_t
     вҚқ              Test_ChiSQ
     вҚқ              Test_Fratio       вҚқ results for A&S tables in: DEFINE_Frat_....
     вҚқ      Check_..  sets up data and runs Stats code.
     вҚқ              Check_MOST_CURVE
     вҚқ              Check_MOST_CURVE
     вҚқ              Check_MOST_FORSY
     вҚқ              Check_MOST_POLYS
     вҚқ              Check_MOST_POLYY
     вҚқ              Check_MOST_REGRE
     вҚқ          err Check_Cheby order
     вҚқ          err Check_Forsythe order
     вҚқ          err Check_Poly order
     вҚқ              Check_Pooling  nm bm fac alpha
     
     вҚқ      Other stuff used by the above and works in progress.
     вҚқ
     вҚқ================================================================================
вҲҮ

вҲҮ NSвҶҗOrthoCalc(x y fp b xty xtx inv xbar ybar names);Divide;yname;xname;bxty;y11y;yty;yhat;errs;sosbo;sosdr;sosar;sostc;sost;dofbo;dofb;doft;ybo;doftc;dofe;msbo;msdr;msar;sesq;serr;fratio;tstat;mrcsq;mrc;seob;max_cov;st_t;pvalues;alpha;list
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   x and y are  the raw data;  b are the regression coefficients
     вҚқвҲҮ   inv is the inverse of the xtx matrix and the ..bar are averages
     
 DivideвҶҗ{({вҚө+вҚө=0}вҚә)Г·{вҚө+0.000001000001Г—вҚө=0}вҚө}
 yname xnameвҶҗ2вҶ‘names
     
 bxtyвҶҗb+.Г—xty
 y11yвҶҗ((+/y)*2)Divideвүўy
 ytyвҶҗy+.Г—y
     
 yhatвҶҗfp+.Г—b
 errsвҶҗy-yhat
     
 sosboвҶҗy11y
 sosdrвҶҗ+/(yhat-ybar)*2
 sosarвҶҗ+/errs*2
 sostcвҶҗ+/(y-ybar)*2
 sostвҶҗyty
     
 yboвҶҗ1         вҚқ  is there to be an intercept
 dofboвҶҗybo
 dofbвҶҗ(вүўb)-ybo
 doftвҶҗ(вүўy)
 doftcвҶҗ(вүўy)-ybo
 dofeвҶҗ1вҢҲdoft-(вүўb)
     
 msboвҶҗsosbo
 msdrвҶҗsosdr Divide dofb
 msarвҶҗsosar Divide dofe
 sesqвҶҗmsar
 serrвҶҗ(|sesq)*0.5
 fratioвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndDP 999999вҢҠ(msdr Divide msar)
 tstatвҶҗserrГ—(|inv)*0.5
     
 mrcsqвҶҗsosdr Divide sostc
 mrcвҶҗ4 ##.Dutils.RndDP((|mrcsq)*0.5)
 seobвҶҗtstat
     
 max_covвҶҗ0
 st_tвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndD b Divide seob
 pvaluesвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndD ##.Distrib.Fratio_AВЁ(|st_t*2),ВЁвҠӮdoftc 1
 alphaвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndD ##.Distrib.Fratio_A fratio dofb dofe
     
 NSвҶҗвҺ•NS''
 listвҶҗ' '(вү вҠҶвҠў)'x y fp b xty xtx inv xbar ybar yname xname bxty y11y yty  yhat errs sosbo sosdr sosar sostc sost dofbo dofb dofe doft doftc msbo msdr msar sesq serr fratio tstat mrcsq mrc seob  max_cov st_t pvalues alpha'
 вҚҺ'NS.(',(вҚ•list),')вҶҗ',вҚ•list
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ nsoвҶҗOrthoOut nsc;b;seob;st_t;nb;Result;u;v;e;s;AnovaT
     
     вҚқвҲҮ make the anova and tabulation tables
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗвҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 nsoвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
 b seob st_tвҶҗnsc.(b seob st_t)
 nbвҶҗвүўb
 ResultвҶҗ((nb+2),6)вҚҙ0
 Result[;1]вҶҗ' i ' '---',(ВҜ1+вҚіnb)
 Result[;2]вҶҗ'         B      ' '  --------------',b
 Result[;3]вҶҗ'    std. err.   ' '  --------------',seob
 Result[;4]вҶҗ'  stud_t' '  ------',st_t
 Result[;5]вҶҗ' F to keep' ' --------',(2 ##.Dutils.RndDP 99999вҢҠst_t*2)
 Result[;6]вҶҗ' Alpha' ' ------',(3 ##.Dutils.RndDP nsc.pvalues)
     
 uвҶҗ'   Sum of Squares ' ' DOF' '    Mean Square  ' '   F ratio ' '   Alpha '
 vвҶҗ'  ----------------' ' ---' '  ---------------' '  ---------' '  -------'
 eвҶҗ'  ================' ' ===' '  ===============' '  =========' '  ======='
 sвҶҗ'        Source  ' ' -----------------' ' constant ' ' due to reg.' ' error   ' ' ==================' ' explained: reg+err ' ' total '
     
     
 AnovaTвҶҗ8 5вҚҙвҠӮ'  '
 AnovaT[1;]вҶҗu
 AnovaT[2;]вҶҗv
 AnovaT[3;]вҶҗ(5 ##.Dutils.RndDP nsc.(sosbo dofbo msbo)),'  ' '  '
 AnovaT[4;]вҶҗ(5 ##.Dutils.RndDP nsc.(sosdr dofb msdr fratio alpha))
 AnovaT[5;]вҶҗ(7 ##.Dutils.RndDP nsc.(sosar dofe msar)),'  ' '  '
 AnovaT[6;]вҶҗe
 AnovaT[7;]вҶҗ(5 ##.Dutils.RndDP nsc.(sostc doftc)),'  ' '  ' '  '
 AnovaT[8;]вҶҗ(5 ##.Dutils.RndDP nsc.(sost doft)),'  ' '  ' '  '
 AnovaTвҶҗs,AnovaT
     
 nso.(Result AnovaT)вҶҗResult AnovaT
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ nssвҶҗOrthoStats nsc;Divide;Rnd;list;N;NT;NB;BIG_E;WB_E;PC_E;BIGPC_E;WB_PCE;INDIV_Z;GIZ;WHICH_BIG;SORT;DURB;EQUAL_VAR;ERR_CORR;ERR_PATRN;NO_RUNS;NO_ABOVE;NO_BELOW;SIGN_RAT;SIGN_MU;SIGN_SIG;SIGN_Z;WHICH_INFL;R_TABLE;R_T;DIGITS_LOST;PERC_EXP;Stats;COOK;WI_C;AP_Q;WI_Q;AP_FIRST;AP_SECOND;AP_STAT;WI_1;WI_2;WI_S;R;SW;in;tr;bp;bod
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  collect results on the data points
     
 DivideвҶҗ{({вҚө+вҚө=0}вҚә)Г·{вҚө+0.000001000001Г—вҚө=0}вҚө}
 RndвҶҗ{вҚҺ30 вҚәвҚ•вҚө}
 nssвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
     вҚқ  this makes the notation for what is in nsc easier
 listвҶҗnsc.вҺ•NL ВҜ2
 вҺ•SHADOW list
 вҚҺ(вҚ•list),'вҶҗnsc.(',(вҚ•list),')'
     
 NвҶҗвүўy
 NTвҶҗ6вҢҠN
 NBвҶҗвүўb
     
 BIG_EвҶҗвҢҲ/|errs
 WB_EвҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|errs
 PC_EвҶҗ3 Rnd 100Г—errs Divide(|yhat)
 BIGPC_EвҶҗвҢҲ/|PC_E
 WB_PCEвҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|PC_E
 INDIV_ZвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndD(errs Divide serr)
 GIZвҶҗвҚӢ|INDIV_Z
 WHICH_BIGвҶҗ(2.5<|INDIV_Z[GIZ])/(вҚіN)[GIZ]
     
 SORTвҶҗerrs[вҚӢyhat]
 DURBвҶҗ2 Rnd(+/((1вҶ“SORT)-(ВҜ1вҶ“SORT))*2)Divide+/SORT*2
     
 EQUAL_VARвҶҗ4 Rnd((ВҜ10000000000вҢҲ10000000000вҢҠerrs)*2)+.Г—(ВҜ10000000000вҢҲ10000000000вҢҠyhat)
 ERR_CORRвҶҗ4 Rnd(errs+.Г—yhat)
 ERR_PATRNвҶҗ4 Rnd(errs+.Г—yhat*2)
 NO_RUNSвҶҗ4 Rnd(1++/(ВҜ1вҶ“errs<0)вү (1вҶ“errs<0))
 NO_ABOVEвҶҗ+/errs>0
 NO_BELOWвҶҗ+/errs<0
 SIGN_RATвҶҗ3 Rnd(NO_ABOVE Divide NO_BELOW+NO_BELOW=0)
 SIGN_MUвҶҗ1+(2Г—NO_ABOVEГ—NO_BELOW)Divide(NO_ABOVE+NO_BELOW)
 SIGN_SIGвҶҗ(2Г—NO_ABOVEГ—NO_BELOW)Г—((2Г—NO_ABOVEГ—NO_BELOW)-(NO_ABOVE+NO_BELOW))Divide(((NO_ABOVE+NO_BELOW)*2)Г—(NO_ABOVE+NO_BELOW-1))
 SIGN_ZвҶҗ2 Rnd(NO_RUNS+0.5-SIGN_MU)Divide SIGN_SIG*0.5
 RвҶҗ1 1вҚүfp+.Г—вҚү(inv)Г—[2]fp
 COOKвҶҗ100Г—((errs Divide serrГ—(|1EВҜ20+1-R)*0.5)*2)Г—(R Divide(1EВҜ20+1-R))Divide NB
 WI_CвҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|COOK
 COOKвҶҗ0 ##.Dutils.RndD(100Г—COOK)
 AP_QвҶҗ10Г—(1EВҜ10вҢҲ|(1 Divide(1EВҜ20+1-R))Г—errs*2)Divide msar
 WI_QвҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|AP_Q
 AP_FIRSTвҶҗ1-(ВҜ10000000000вҢҲ10000000000вҢҠAP_Q)Divide(1EВҜ10вҢҲsosar)
 AP_SECONDвҶҗ1-R
 AP_STATвҶҗAP_FIRSTГ—AP_SECOND
 AP_QвҶҗ0 ##.Dutils.RndD AP_Q
 AP_FIRSTвҶҗ0 ##.Dutils.RndD(100Г—1-AP_FIRST)
 WI_1вҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|AP_FIRST
 AP_SECONDвҶҗ0 ##.Dutils.RndD(100Г—1-AP_SECOND)
 WI_2вҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|AP_SECOND
 AP_STATвҶҗ0 ##.Dutils.RndD(100Г—1-AP_STAT)
 WI_SвҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|AP_STAT
     
 WHICH_INFLвҶҗ(1вҶ‘WB_E)(1вҶ‘WB_PCE)(1вҶ‘WI_C)(1вҶ‘WI_Q)(1вҶ‘WI_1)(1вҶ‘WI_2)(1вҶ‘WI_S)
     
 R_TABLEвҶҗ(вҚіN),вҢҪAP_STAT,AP_SECOND,AP_FIRST,AP_Q,COOK,INDIV_Z,PC_E,errs,yhat,y,[1.5]x
     
 R_TвҶҗ2 ##.Dutils.RndPВЁR_TABLE
 R_TвҶҗ(вҚі12),[1](вҚі12),[1]R_T
 R_T[1;]вҶҗ' i ' '    x ' '    y ' ' y_hat' ' resid' ' % err' ' res_z' ' Cook ' 'AP q' 'AP 1' 'AP 2' ' AP '
 R_T[2;]вҶҗ'---' '------' '------' '------' '------' '------' '------' '------' '----' '----' '----' '----'
     
 ERR_CORRвҶҗ4 Rnd(ERR_CORRГ—0.000001<|ERR_CORR)
 PERC_EXPвҶҗ2 Rnd(100Г—mrcsq)
     
 DIGITS_LOSTвҶҗ0
 :Trap 0
     inвҶҗвҢ№(вҚүfp)+.Г—fp
     trвҶҗ1 1вҚүin
     bpвҶҗвҢҲ/|tr
     inГ·вҶҗbp
     (1 1вҚүin)вҶҗ0
     bodвҶҗвҢҲ/,|in
     DIGITS_LOSTвҶҗ0вҢҲ17+10вҚҹ|bod
 :EndTrap
     
 SWвҶҗ110
 StatsвҶҗ27 SWвҚҙ' '
 Stats[1;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'equal var. stat.       ',вҚ•EQUAL_VAR
 Stats[2;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'correl. error stat.    ',вҚ•ERR_CORR
 Stats[3;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'patterned err. stat.   ',вҚ•ERR_PATRN
 Stats[4;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'no. positive errors    ',вҚ•NO_ABOVE
 Stats[5;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'no. negative errors    ',вҚ•NO_BELOW
 Stats[6;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'error sign ratio       ',вҚ•SIGN_RAT
 Stats[7;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'sign pattern z         ',вҚ•SIGN_Z
 Stats[8;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'               influential residuals: mostвҶ’less '
 Stats[9;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'largest residuals      ',6 0вҚ•WB_E
 Stats[10;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'largest % residuals    ',6 0вҚ•WB_PCE
 Stats[11;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'   (outliers)  Q       ',6 0вҚ•WI_Q
 Stats[12;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'   (outliers)  AP 1    ',6 0вҚ•WI_1
 Stats[13;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'   (remote)    AP 2    ',6 0вҚ•WI_2
 Stats[14;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'   (AP1Г—AP2)   AP      ',6 0вҚ•WI_S
 Stats[15;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'   (coeffnts.) Cook    ',6 0вҚ•WI_C
 Stats[16;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'biggest covariance     ',вҚ•max_cov
 Stats[17;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘' '
 Stats[18;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'big err. : index       ',(вҚ•BIG_E),' : ',4 0вҚ•1вҶ‘WB_E
 Stats[19;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'big % err. : index     ',(вҚ•BIGPC_E),' : ',4 0вҚ•1вҶ‘WB_PCE
 Stats[20;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'errors having z>2.5    ',6 0вҚ•WHICH_BIG
 Stats[21;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'Durbin Watson stat.    ',вҚ•DURB
 Stats[22;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'digits lost            ',вҚ•DIGITS_LOST
 Stats[23;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'multpl. reg. coeff.    ',вҚ•mrc
 Stats[24;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'% var. explained       ',вҚ•PERC_EXP
 Stats[25;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'std. err. (sigma)      ',вҚ•serr
 Stats[26;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'total variance in y    ',вҚ•sostcГ·N
 Stats[27;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'unexplained var.       ',вҚ•sosarГ·N
     
 nss.StatsвҶҗStats
 nss.ResidTableвҶҗR_T
 nss.DLвҶҗDIGITS_LOST
     вҚқ EOR
вҲҮ

вҲҮ TвҶҗRandNorm N;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ t вҶҗ вҲҶRANDN n  --  deliver n normally distributed random numbers:
     вҚқвҲҮ     в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ           mean=0, std=1
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 TвҶҗ(2в—Ӣв—Ӣ2Г—?NвҚҙ0)Г—0.5*вҚЁ-2Г—вҚҹ?NвҚҙ0
 :Return
     
     
     вҚқ===============================================================
     вҚқ    three times slower on a million numbers
 TвҶҗNвҚҙ0
 :For I :In вҚі12
     T+вҶҗ?NвҚҙ0
 :EndFor
 TвҶҗT-6
     
     
     вҚқ    five times slower yet than that on a million numbers:  15x slower
 TвҶҗNвҚҙ0
 :For I :In вҚіN
     T[I]вҶҗВҜ6++/?12вҚҙ0
 :EndFor
 TвҶҗT-6
     
     вҚқ    untimed: (but it takes up a lot of space!!!)
 TвҶҗ6-+/N 12вҚҙ?(12Г—N)вҚҙ0
вҲҮ

вҲҮ NSвҶҗRegressCalc(x y b xty xtx inv xbar ybar ib names);Divide;yname;xnames;bxty;y11y;yty;yhat;errs;sosbo;sosdr;sosar;sostc;sost;dofbo;dofb;dofe;doft;doftc;msbo;msdr;msar;sesq;serr;fratio;tstat;mrcsq;mrc;seob;trc;denom;req;covr;bigcv;max_cov;st_t;list;pvalues;alpha;r
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   x and y are  the raw data;  b are the regression coefficients
     вҚқвҲҮ   inv is the inverse of the xtx matrix and the ..bar are averages
     
 DivideвҶҗ{({вҚө+вҚө=0}вҚә)Г·{вҚө+0.000001000001Г—вҚө=0}вҚө}
 ynameвҶҗвҠғnames
 xnamesвҶҗ1вҶ“names
     
 bxtyвҶҗb+.Г—xty
 y11yвҶҗ((+/y)*2)Divideвүўy
 ytyвҶҗy+.Г—y
     
 yhatвҶҗx+.Г—b
 errsвҶҗy-yhat
     
 sosboвҶҗy11y
 sosdrвҶҗ+/(yhat-ybar)*2
 sosarвҶҗ+/errs*2
 sostcвҶҗ+/(y-ybar)*2
 sostвҶҗyty
     
 dofboвҶҗвҲ§/x[;1]=1
 dofbвҶҗ(вүўb)-dofbo
 dofeвҶҗ(вүўy)-вүўb
 doftвҶҗвүўy
 doftcвҶҗdoft-dofbo
     
 msboвҶҗsosbo
 msdrвҶҗsosdr Divide dofb
 msarвҶҗsosar Divide dofe
 sesqвҶҗmsar
 serrвҶҗ(|sesq)*0.5
 fratioвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndDP 999999вҢҠ(msdr Divide msar)
 tstatвҶҗserrГ—(|inv)*0.5
 mrcsqвҶҗsosdr Divide sostc
 mrcвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndDP((|mrcsq)*0.5)
 seobвҶҗ1 1вҚүtstat
     
 trcвҶҗ1000000000000000вҢҠВҜ1000000000000000вҢҲ1 1вҚүinv
 denomвҶҗtrcвҲҳ.Г—trc
 denomвҶҗ(denom=0)+(denomГ—denomвү 0)
 reqвҶҗinv Divide(|denom)*0.5
 covrвҶҗ4 ##.Dutils.RndDPВЁ(req-ib)
 bigcvвҶҗвҢҲ/|covr
 max_covвҶҗвҢҲ/|bigcv
 st_tвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndDP b Divide seob
 pvaluesвҶҗ##.Distrib.Student_AВЁ(|st_t),ВЁdoftc
 alphaвҶҗ##.Distrib.Fratio_A fratio dofb dofe
     
 NSвҶҗвҺ•NS''
 listвҶҗ' '(вү вҠҶвҠў)'x y b xty xtx inv xbar ybar ib yname xnames bxty y11y yty yhat errs sosbo sosdr sosar sostc sost dofbo dofb dofe doft doftc msbo msdr msar sesq serr fratio tstat mrcsq mrc seob trc denom req covr bigcv max_cov st_t pvalues alpha'
 вҚҺ'NS.(',(вҚ•list),')вҶҗ',вҚ•list
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ NSRвҶҗRegressResults NSC;pvalues;nb;nd;T;U;E;S;Result;AnovaR
     
 NSRвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
 nbвҶҗвүўNSC.b вӢ„ ndвҶҗвүўNSC.y
 ResultвҶҗ((nb+2),8)вҚҙ0
 Result[;1]вҶҗ' i ' '---',(ВҜ1+вҚіnb)
 Result[;2]вҶҗ'         B      ' '  -------------',13 ##.Dutils.RndDPВЁNSC.b
 Result[;3]вҶҗ'    std. err.   ' '  -------------',8 ##.Dutils.RndDPВЁNSC.seob
 Result[;4]вҶҗ'  stud_t' '  ------',2 ##.Dutils.RndDP NSC.st_t
 Result[;5]вҶҗ' alpha P' '  ------',3 ##.Dutils.RndDP NSC.pvalues
 Result[;6]вҶҗ' max.cov.' ' --------',NSC.bigcv
 Result[;7]вҶҗ' F-remove' ' --------',3 ##.Dutils.RndDP 99999вҢҠ(NSC.st_t*2)
 Result[;8]вҶҗ' Alpha' ' --------',3 ##.Dutils.RndDP ##.Distrib.Fratio_AВЁ(|NSC.st_t*2),ВЁвҠӮ1 NSC.dofe
     
     
 TвҶҗ'          Sum of Squares' '  DOF' '           Mean Square  ' '   F ratio ' '   Alpha '
 UвҶҗ' -----------------------' ' ----' ' -----------------------' '  ---------' '  -------'
 EвҶҗ' =======================' ' ====' ' =======================' '  =========' '   '
 SвҶҗ'    Source  ' '  ----------' ' constant ' ' due to reg.' ' error   ' ' ===========' ' total corr.' ' uncorrected'
 AnovaRвҶҗ8 5вҚҙвҠӮ'  '
 AnovaR[1;]вҶҗT
 AnovaR[2;]вҶҗU
 AnovaR[3;]вҶҗ(3 ##.Dutils.RndDP NSC.sosbo),NSC.dofbo,(3 ##.Dutils.RndDP NSC.msbo),'  ' '  '
 AnovaR[4;]вҶҗ(3 ##.Dutils.RndDP NSC.sosdr),NSC.dofb,(3 ##.Dutils.RndDP NSC.msdr),(NSC.fratio),(4 ##.Dutils.RndDP NSC.alpha)
 AnovaR[5;]вҶҗ(3 ##.Dutils.RndDP NSC.sosar),NSC.dofe,(3 ##.Dutils.RndDP NSC.msar),'  ' '  '
 AnovaR[6;]вҶҗE
 AnovaR[7;]вҶҗ(3 ##.Dutils.RndDP NSC.sostc),NSC.doftc,'  ' '  ' '  '
 AnovaR[8;]вҶҗ(3 ##.Dutils.RndDP NSC.sost),NSC.doft,'  ' '  ' '  '
 AnovaRвҶҗS,AnovaR
     
 NSR.ResultвҶҗResult
 NSR.AnovaRвҶҗAnovaR
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ NSSвҶҗdl RegressStats NSC;Divide;Rnd;list;N;NT;NB;BIG_E;WB_E;PC_E;BIGPC_E;WB_PCE;INDIV_Z;GIZ;WHICH_BIG;SORT;DURB;EQUAL_VAR;ERR_CORR;ERR_PATRN;NO_RUNS;NO_ABOVE;NO_BELOW;SIGN_RAT;SIGN_MU;SIGN_SIG;SIGN_Z;TRACE;COOK;WI_C;AP_Q;WI_Q;AP_FIRST;AP_SECOND;AP_STAT;WI_1;WI_2;WI_S;WHICH_INFL;R_TABLE;R_T;DIGITS_LOST;PERC_EXP;SW;Stats
     
 DivideвҶҗ{({вҚө+вҚө=0}вҚә)Г·{вҚө+0.000001000001Г—вҚө=0}вҚө}
 RndвҶҗ{вҚҺ30 вҚәвҚ•вҚө}
 NSSвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
 listвҶҗNSC.вҺ•NL ВҜ2
 вҺ•SHADOW list
 вҚҺ(вҚ•list),'вҶҗNSC.(',(вҚ•list),')'
     
 NвҶҗвүўy
 NTвҶҗ20вҢҠN
 NBвҶҗвүўb
 BIG_EвҶҗвҢҲ/|errs
 WB_EвҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|errs
 PC_EвҶҗ100Г—errs Divide|yhat
 PC_EвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndD PC_E
 BIGPC_EвҶҗвҢҲ/|PC_E
 WB_PCEвҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|PC_E
 INDIV_ZвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndD(errs Divide serr)
 GIZвҶҗвҚ’|INDIV_Z
 WHICH_BIGвҶҗ(2.5<|INDIV_Z[GIZ])/(вҚіN)[GIZ]
 :If NB>1 вӢ„ SORTвҶҗerrs[вҚӢx[;2]] вӢ„ :EndIf
 :If NBвүӨ1 вӢ„ SORTвҶҗerrs[вҚӢyhat] вӢ„ :EndIf
 DURBвҶҗ2 ##.Dutils.RndD(+/((1вҶ“SORT)-(ВҜ1вҶ“SORT))*2)Divide+/SORT*2
 EQUAL_VARвҶҗ4 ##.Dutils.RndD((ВҜ10000000000вҢҲ10000000000вҢҠerrs)*2)+.Г—(ВҜ10000000000вҢҲ10000000000вҢҠyhat)
 ERR_CORRвҶҗ4 ##.Dutils.RndD(errs+.Г—yhat)
 ERR_PATRNвҶҗ4 ##.Dutils.RndD(errs+.Г—yhat*2)
 NO_RUNSвҶҗ4 ##.Dutils.RndD(1++/(ВҜ1вҶ“SORT<0)вү (1вҶ“SORT<0))
 NO_ABOVEвҶҗ+/errs>0
 NO_BELOWвҶҗ+/errs<0
 SIGN_RATвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndD(NO_ABOVE Divide{вҚө+вҚө=0}NO_BELOW)
 SIGN_MUвҶҗ1+(2Г—NO_ABOVEГ—NO_BELOW)Divide(NO_ABOVE+NO_BELOW)
 SIGN_SIGвҶҗ(2Г—NO_ABOVEГ—NO_BELOW)Г—((2Г—NO_ABOVEГ—NO_BELOW)-(NO_ABOVE+NO_BELOW))Divide(((NO_ABOVE+NO_BELOW)*2)Г—(NO_ABOVE+NO_BELOW-1))
 SIGN_ZвҶҗ2 ##.Dutils.RndD(NO_RUNS+0.5-SIGN_MU)Divide SIGN_SIG*0.5
     
 TRACEвҶҗ1 1вҚүx+.Г—(inv)+.Г—вҚүx
     
 COOKвҶҗ100Г—((errs Divide serrГ—(|1EВҜ20+1-TRACE)*0.5)*2)Г—(TRACE Divide(1EВҜ20+1-TRACE))Divide NB
 WI_CвҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|COOK
 AP_QвҶҗ10Г—(1EВҜ10вҢҲ|(1 Divide(1EВҜ20+1-TRACE))Г—errs*2)Divide msar
 WI_QвҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|AP_Q
 AP_FIRSTвҶҗ1-(ВҜ10000000000вҢҲ10000000000вҢҠAP_Q)Divide(1EВҜ10вҢҲsosar)
 AP_SECONDвҶҗ1-TRACE
 AP_STATвҶҗAP_FIRSTГ—AP_SECOND
 COOKвҶҗ0 ##.Dutils.RndD(100Г—COOK)
 AP_QвҶҗ0 ##.Dutils.RndD AP_Q
 AP_FIRSTвҶҗ0 ##.Dutils.RndD(100Г—1-AP_FIRST)
 WI_1вҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|AP_FIRST
 AP_SECONDвҶҗ0 ##.Dutils.RndD(100Г—1-AP_SECOND)
 WI_2вҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|AP_SECOND
 AP_STATвҶҗ0 ##.Dutils.RndD(100Г—1-AP_STAT)
 WI_SвҶҗNTвҶ‘вҚ’|AP_STAT
     
 WHICH_INFLвҶҗ(1вҶ‘WB_E)(1вҶ‘WB_PCE)(1вҶ‘WI_C)(1вҶ‘WI_Q)(1вҶ‘WI_1)(1вҶ‘WI_2)(1вҶ‘WI_S)
     
     
 R_TABLEвҶҗ(вҚіN),вҢҪAP_STAT,AP_SECOND,AP_FIRST,AP_Q,COOK,INDIV_Z,PC_E,errs,yhat,y,x[;,2вҢҠNB]
     
 R_TвҶҗ2 ##.Dutils.RndDВЁR_TABLE
 R_TвҶҗ(вҚі12),[1](вҚі12),[1]R_T
