 Stats[3;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'patterned err. stat.   ',вҚ•ERR_PATRN
 Stats[4;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'no. positive errors    ',вҚ•NO_ABOVE
 Stats[5;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'no. negative errors    ',вҚ•NO_BELOW
 Stats[6;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'error sign ratio       ',вҚ•SIGN_RAT
 Stats[7;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'sign pattern z         ',вҚ•SIGN_Z
 Stats[8;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'               influential residuals: mostвҶ’less '
 Stats[9;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'largest residuals      ',6 0вҚ•WB_E
 Stats[10;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'largest % residuals    ',6 0вҚ•WB_PCE
 Stats[11;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'   (outliers)  Q       ',6 0вҚ•WI_Q
 Stats[12;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'   (outliers)  AP 1    ',6 0вҚ•WI_1
 Stats[13;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'   (remote)    AP 2    ',6 0вҚ•WI_2
 Stats[14;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'   (AP1Г—AP2)   AP      ',6 0вҚ•WI_S
 Stats[15;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'   (coeffnts.) Cook    ',6 0вҚ•WI_C
 Stats[16;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'biggest covariance     ',вҚ•max_cov
 Stats[17;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘' '
 Stats[18;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'big err. : index       ',(вҚ•BIG_E),' : ',4 0вҚ•1вҶ‘WB_E
 Stats[19;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'big % err. : index     ',(вҚ•BIGPC_E),' : ',4 0вҚ•1вҶ‘WB_PCE
 Stats[20;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'errors having z>2.5    ',6 0вҚ•WHICH_BIG
 Stats[21;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'Durbin Watson stat.    ',вҚ•DURB
 Stats[22;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'digits lost            ',вҚ•DIGITS_LOST
 Stats[23;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'multpl. reg. coeff.    ',вҚ•mrc
 Stats[24;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'% var. explained       ',вҚ•PERC_EXP
 Stats[25;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'std. err. (sigma)      ',вҚ•serr
 Stats[26;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'total variance in y    ',вҚ•sostcГ·N
 Stats[27;]вҶҗSWвҶ‘'unexplained var.       ',вҚ•sosarГ·N
     
 NSS.StatsвҶҗStats
 NSS.ResidTableвҶҗR_T
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ cleanвҶҗ{what}RemoveExcessBlanks vector;Rem
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  remove extraneous blanks/w:  i    am => i am
     вҚқвҲҮ        'MISISIPPI' вҶҗ 'S' RemoveExcessBlanks 'MISSISSIPPI'
     вҚқвҲҮ          3 0 4 0 5 вҶҗ RemoveExcessBlanks 0 0 3 0 0 0 0 4 0 0 0 5 0 0 0 0
     вҚқвҲҮ    'this is clean' вҶҗ RemoveExcessBlanks '   this  is clean    '
     
 :If 0=вҺ•NC'what' вӢ„ whatвҶҗвҠғ1вҶ‘0вҚҙ,vector вӢ„ :EndIf вҚқ  either ' '  or 0
     
 RemвҶҗ{1вҶ“вҚә{{вҚөвҲЁ1вҢҪвҚө}вҚөвү вҚә}вҚә,вҚө}
 cleanвҶҗ(what Rem vector)/vector
     вҚқ pull of all leading what's
 cleanвҶҗ(~1вҶ“вҲ§\(what,clean)вҲҠwhat)/clean
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ zвҶҗd RndD v;вҺ•IO;f
     
     вҚқвҲҮ round to a number of decimal places:  12.235  вҶҗ  3 RndD 12.2345678
     
 :If (vвүЎвҚ¬) вӢ„ zвҶҗv вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf
 вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 :If 2вүӨвҚҙвҚҙv вӢ„ zвҶҗ(вҚҙv)вҚҙd RndD,v вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf
     
 fвҶҗ10*d
 zвҶҗ(вҢҠ0.5+fГ—v)Г·f
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ zвҶҗn RndDP v
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  round to a given no. of decimal places by formatting:  23.35  вҶҗ  2 RndDP  23.34567
     
 :If 2вүӨвҚҙвҚҙv вӢ„ zвҶҗ(вҚҙv)вҚҙn RndDP,v вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf
     
 :Trap 0
     zвҶҗвҚҺ30 nвҚ•v
 :Else
     zвҶҗвҚ¬
 :EndTrap
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ zвҶҗn RndF v;b;d
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  round the vector to match the largest value's decimal to n decimal places
     
 bвҶҗвҢҲ/|,v
 dвҶҗn-вҢҲ10вҚҹ(b+b=0)
 zвҶҗd RndD v
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ zвҶҗp RndP v
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  round to a given decimal places pattern:   23.35  вҶҗ  .01 RndP  23.34567
     
 zвҶҗ(Г—v)Г—pГ—вҢҠ0.5+|vГ·p
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ rвҶҗn RndS v;k
     
     вҚқвҲҮ round to n significant digits:  1235000  вҶҗ 4 RndS 1234567.89
     
 kвҶҗ10*1-n-вҢҠ10вҚҹ|v+v=0
 rвҶҗ(vвү 0)Г—kГ—вҢҠ0.5+vГ·k
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ zвҶҗn Rndp z;m
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  round to a number of decimal places:
 mвҶҗ10*n
 zвҶҗ(вҢҠ0.5+mГ—z)Г·m
     
 :Return
