 wвҶҗвҺ•VR'Watcher'
 wвҶҗ'down left' '3.3 .2'вҲҶREPLACE_STRING w
 wвҶҗ'Watcher_base' 'Watcher 'вҲҶREPLACE_STRING w
 вҺ•FX w
