вҲҮ fixedвҶҗold_new вҲҶREPLACE_STRING string;old;new;j
     
     вҚқвҲҮ fixedвҶҗ'old' 'new' вҲҶREPLACE_STRING cvec -- replace occurances of 'old' in cvec
     вҚқвҲҮ                   в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ         with new
     вҚқвҲҮ
     вҚқвҲҮ    cvec must be a character vector
     вҚқвҲҮ    old and new must be scalars or vectors of characters
     
     
 old newвҶҗ,ВЁ2вҶ‘old_new
     
 jвҶҗoldвҚ·string
 fixedвҶҗ(вҚҙnew)вҶ“вҠғ,/((вҚҙstring)вҚҙвҠӮnew),ВЁ(вҚҙold)вҶ“ВЁstringвҶҗ(((вҚҙold)вҶ‘1),j)вҠӮold,string
вҲҮ

вҲҮ zвҶҗ(FunX HalfStep)ABN;a;b;n;ya;yb;yz;i;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO

вҚқвҲҮ trial and error by half_stepping:  if you start correctly bracketed
вҚқвҲҮ it will always converge
вҚқвҲҮ    argument:  two values of X that with have a funtion result of
вҚқвҲҮ               opposite sign and the max number of steps (20 will
вҚқвҲҮ               reduce the uncertainty to one-millionth of the A-B
вҚқвҲҮ               gap.  default to 53 == 16 digits).

 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 a b nвҶҗ3вҶ‘ABN,53

 zвҶҗa
 yaвҶҗFunX z
 :If ya=0 вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf
 zвҶҗb
 ybвҶҗFunX z
 :If yb=0 вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf

вҚқ  Check for bracketing
 zвҶҗ1
 :If 0<yaГ—yb вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf

 вҚқ  start halving
 :For i :In вҚіn
     zвҶҗ0.5Г—a+b
     yzвҶҗFunX z
вҚқ      'half'##.Dutils.Watcher i':'ya yz yb':'a z b
     :If yz=0 вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf  вҚқ  may as well quit with an exact root
     :If 0<yzГ—ya    вҚқ  yz is on the same side as ya
         a yaвҶҗz yz
     :Else
         b ybвҶҗz yz
     :EndIf
 :EndFor

 вҚқ  accept z

 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ zвҶҗ(FunX HalfStepI)ABN;a;b;n;ya;yb;yz;i;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO

вҚқвҲҮ trial and error by half_stepping:  if you start correctly bracketed
вҚқвҲҮ it will always converge
вҚқвҲҮ    argument:  two values of X that with have a funtion result of
вҚқвҲҮ               opposite sign and the max number of steps (20 will
вҚқвҲҮ               reduce the uncertainty to one-millionth of the A-B
вҚқвҲҮ               gap.  default to 53 == 16 digits).

 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 a b nвҶҗ3вҶ‘ABN,53

 zвҶҗa
 yaвҶҗFunX z
 :If ya=0 вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf
 zвҶҗb
 ybвҶҗFunX z
 :If yb=0 вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf

вҚқ  Check for bracketing
 zвҶҗвҚ¬
 :If 0<yaГ—yb вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf

 вҚқ  start halving
 :For i :In вҚіn
     zвҶҗвҢҲ0.5Г—a+b
     yzвҶҗFunX z
     :If yz=0 вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf  вҚқ  may as well quit with an exact root
     :If 0<yzГ—ya    вҚқ  yz is on the same side as ya
         a yaвҶҗz yz
     :Else
         b ybвҶҗz yz
     :EndIf
     :If 1=|a-b вӢ„ :Leave вӢ„ :EndIf
 :EndFor


 вҚқ  accept the better of ya yb
 zвҶҗa
 :If </|yb ya вӢ„ zвҶҗb вӢ„ :EndIf

 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ ZвҶҗ(F Romberg_Trap)(low_lim high_lim);Improve;x;sum;вҲҶx;nx;xn;A;B;C;D;n;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO

вҚқвҲҮ   Apply Romberg technique to integration based on trapazoidal quadrature:
вҚқвҲҮ      if an integrator has an order n with a step size of h, and two areas
вҚқвҲҮ      are computed at 2h and h (Ab As) then an improved value can be had:
вҚқвҲҮ      Ai вҶҗ (2*n)As - Ab Г· (2*n - 1)

вҚқ  the trapazoidal integration is A1 вҶҗ .5 Г— (B-A)Г— +/FВЁ A B  for one step
вҚқ  but at more steps it is   sumвҶҗ+/.5 1 1 1 ... 1 1 1 .5 Г— FВЁx  and AвҶҗвҲҶxГ—sum
вҚқ  at the next interval halving вҲҶxвҶҗ.5Г—вҲҶx and  sumвҶҗsum+FВЁx at the mid-points
вҚқ  therefore: keep track of x, sum, вҲҶx
вҚқ  experiments indicate that C is far enough

 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 ImproveвҶҗ{((dГ—2вҠғвҚө)-вҠғвҚө)Г·ВҜ1+dвҶҗ2*вҚә}
 xвҶҗlow_lim high_lim
 sumвҶҗ0.5Г—+/FВЁx
 вҲҶxвҶҗhigh_lim-low_lim
 nвҶҗ1
 AвҶҗвҲҶxГ—sum
 BвҶҗCвҶҗDвҶҗвҚ¬

 :Repeat
     nГ—вҶҗ2
     вҲҶxвҶҗ0.5Г—вҲҶx
     nxвҶҗВҜ1+вүўx
     xnвҶҗlow_lim+(2Г—вҲҶxГ—вҚіnx)-вҲҶx
     sum+вҶҗSumByTwos FВЁxn
     xвҶҗlow_lim+вҲҶxГ—0,вҚі2Г—nx
     A,вҶҗвҲҶxГ—sum
     B,вҶҗ2 Improve ВҜ2вҶ‘A
     :If 2вүӨвүўB вӢ„ C,вҶҗ4 Improve ВҜ2вҶ‘B вӢ„ :EndIf
вҚқ      :If 2вүӨвүўC вӢ„ D,вҶҗ8 Improve ВҜ2вҶ‘C вӢ„ :EndIf
 :Until n>1000000
 :OrIf (=/ВҜ2вҶ‘B)вҲ§(2вүӨвүўB)
 :OrIf (=/ВҜ2вҶ‘C)вҲ§(2вүӨвүўC)
 ZвҶҗвҠғвҢҪC
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ AREAвҶҗ(F вҲҶGQ)CH;C;H

вҚқвҲҮ Gauss Quadrature
вҚқвҲҮ area вҶҗ f вҲҶGQ c h -- do one panel integration using GLOBALS: QZ QW
вҚқвҲҮ          в”Җв”Җв”Җ        a panel is defined by its center and halfwidth

 C HвҶҗCH
 :If 0=вҺ•NC'QW' вӢ„ DEFINE_QW вӢ„ DEFINE_QZ вӢ„ :EndIf
 AREAвҶҗHГ—+/QWГ—FВЁC+QZГ—H

 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ AREAвҶҗ(FQ вҲҶQUAD)ABN;A;B;N;C;H
вҚқ     %&%    6:57:41 AM Monday, July 20, 1998        fwk

вҚқвҲҮ area вҶҗ((f qmethod) вҲҶQUAD) a b no_of_panels -- do a whole integral of f
вҚқвҲҮ                     в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ                     from a to b using the
вҚқвҲҮ                                               supplied quadrature algo.

 A B NвҶҗABN
 HвҶҗ(B-A)Г·NГ—2
 CвҶҗ(A-H)+2Г—HГ—вҚіN

 AREAвҶҗ+/FQВЁC,ВЁH
вҲҮ

:Namespace XвҲҶWATCHER
(вҺ•IO вҺ•ML вҺ•WX вҺ•PP)вҶҗ1 1 3 8

:EndNamespace 
:EndNamespace 
:Namespace NS
(вҺ•IO вҺ•ML вҺ•WX)вҶҗ1 1 3

:EndNamespace 
