вҲҮ {NS}вҶҗAnova args;Trim;nfact;nrep;levels;comb;ncells;ndata;average;delta;ave;sostotal;doftotal;array;cells;cell_ave;deltas;sos_err;ms_err;i_effects;c_effects;n_effects;inl;ca;sos;dof;ms;frat;hi;df;i;outs;ins;nave;mult;crot;crave;corr;wcorr;mserrd;alfa;dof_err;got;tit;equ;ans;doferrd;err;tot;min;eql;data;n_levels;norm;nrows;rave;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  Create and ANalysis Of VAriance table given:
     вҚқвҲҮ     data: a vector of the data with replicates going the fastest
     вҚқвҲҮ           (last logical subscript), and the first factor (A)
     вҚқвҲҮ           going the slowest (first logical subscript).
     вҚқвҲҮ           If the data is a logical multimentional array:
     вҚқвҲҮ                data вҶҗ ,ARRAY[A;B;C;......;Reps]
     вҚқвҲҮ     n_levels:  number of levels of each factor
     вҚқвҲҮ              e.g.: for  ARRAYвҶҗ3 5 4 7 2 вҚҙ data
     вҚқвҲҮ                      n_levelsвҶҗ3 5 4 7 2
     вҚқвҲҮ                      factorsвҶҗ4 :: factor levels = 3 5 4 7
     вҚқвҲҮ                      number of replicates = 2
     вҚқвҲҮ                      factor D has 7 levels
     вҚқвҲҮ              no factor should have just 0 or 1 level; but there
     вҚқвҲҮ              can be just 1 replicate
     вҚқвҲҮ     norm:  if =1 the table will be put in "normal" order: A  B AB  C AC BC ABC   D AD .....
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 TrimвҶҗ{{вҚҺ(25 10вҚ•вҚө)~'_'}ВЁвҚө}
 NSвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
 data n_levels normвҶҗ3вҶ‘args,0
 NS.ANOVA_DataвҶҗdata
     
 nfactвҶҗВҜ1+вүўn_levels
 nrepвҶҗвҠғвҢҪn_levels
 levelsвҶҗВҜ1вҶ“n_levels
 :If вҲЁ/levels<2 вӢ„ 'Can not have 0 or 1 as a number of items in a factor.' вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf
     
 combвҶҗ##.Dutils.CompleteComb nfact             вҚқ  let the term effect refer to: main effects (A, B, ..) and the interactions (AB, ... ACD, ...)
 ncellsвҶҗГ—/levels
     
 ndataвҶҗГ—/n_levels
 :If ndataвүўвүўdata вӢ„ 'data length '(вүўdata)' does not match levels '(ndata) вӢ„ :Return вӢ„ :EndIf
     
 aveвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwos data[ndata?ndata])Г·ndata            вҚқ  add up the data in random order as carefully as possible
 averageвҶҗave+ndataГ·вҚЁ##.Dutils.SumByTwos data-ave              вҚқ  refine the average as the average + the average of the residuals (which should be close to zero)
 deltasвҶҗdata-average
     
     вҚқ   start collecting info
 sostotalвҶҗ+/deltas*2
 doftotalвҶҗndata-1
     вҚқ   make an array
 cellsвҶҗn_levelsвҚҙdeltas
 cell_aveвҶҗ(+/cells)Г·nrep             вҚқ average across the replicates foe each cell
 residualsвҶҗdeltas-,cell_aveвҲҳ.Г—nrepвҚҙ1
 sos_errвҶҗ+/residuals*2               вҚқ this should be zero if there are just 1 replicates
 dof_errвҶҗncellsГ—nrep-1
 ms_errвҶҗsos_errГ·{вҚө+вҚө=0}dof_err       вҚқ is this 0 if there is but 1 replicate
     
     вҚқ generate the anova items (single effects, plus interactions
 i_effectsвҶҗ,[1.5]##.Dutils.CompleteComb nfact   вҚқ  column matrix of factor indexes
 c_effectsвҶҗвҺ•AвҲҳ{вҚә[вҚө]}ВЁi_effects        вҚқ  character representation of the effects;  A B ... ABD ...
 n_effectsвҶҗвүўi_effects                 вҚқ  how many rows in the anova table
 inlвҶҗвҚіnfact                           вҚқ  1 2 ... no-of-factors
     
 caвҶҗ(вҚҙi_effects)вҚҙ0                    вҚқ  m 2  matrix
 sosвҶҗdofвҶҗmsвҶҗfratвҶҗn_effectsвҚҙ0          вҚқ  start them out as zeros
     
 hiвҶҗn_effects                         вҚқ table row-index of the highest interaction
 ca[hi;1]вҶҗвҠӮcell_ave+average
 sos[hi]вҶҗ+/,cell_ave*2
 dof[hi]вҶҗГ—/levels-1
 ms[hi]вҶҗsos[hi]Г·dof[hi]
     
     вҚқ  process all of the effects
 :For i :In ВҜ1вҶ“вҚіn_effects             вҚқ  highest interaction has no insis a special case
     outsвҶҗiвҠғi_effects[;1]            вҚқ  axes that will have their sums calculated
     insвҶҗinl~outs                    вҚқ  sum over all of these axes
     dof[i]вҶҗdfвҶҗГ—/n_levels[outs]-1
     naveвҶҗГ—/n_levels[ins]
     multвҶҗnrepГ—Г—/n_levels[ins]
     
     crotвҶҗTrim(вҠғ,/n_levels[outs],nave)вҚҙ(вҚӢ,вҠғ,/(outs,ins))вҚүcell_ave  вҚқ
     craveвҶҗTrim(+/crot)Г·nave
     ca[i;1]вҶҗвҠӮcrave+average
     corrвҶҗwcorrвҶҗ0
     
     :If i>1
         wcorrвҶҗ~вҲЁвҢҝinsвҲҳ.вҲҠ(i-1)вҶ‘,i_effects        вҚқ  which previous effects contain a current "in"
         corrвҶҗTrim+/wcorr/sos[вҚіi-1]
     :EndIf
     sos[i]вҶҗTrim(multГ—+/,(crave)*2)-corr
     ms[i]вҶҗTrim sos[i]Г·df
     :If i>nfact
     
     :EndIf
 :EndFor
     
 iвҶҗn_effects
 ca[i;1]вҶҗвҠӮcell_ave+average
 sos[i]вҶҗTrim 0вҢҲ(nrepГ—+/,cell_ave*2)-+/sos[вҚіi-1]
 ms[i]вҶҗTrim 0вҢҲsos[i]Г·dof[i]
     
 mserrdвҶҗms_err
 doferrdвҶҗdof_err
 :If dof_err=0
     mserrdвҶҗ0вҢҲms[n_effects]
     doferrdвҶҗdof[n_effects]
     ms_errвҶҗ0
 :EndIf
 mserrdвҶҗTrim mserrd
 doferrdвҶҗ{вҚө+вҚө=0}doferrd
 fratвҶҗmsГ·{вҚө+вҚө=0}mserrd
 alfaвҶҗ{{вҚҺ15 3вҚ•вҚө}ВЁвҚө}##.Distrib.Fratio_AВЁfrat,ВЁdof,ВЁdoferrd
     
 fratвҶҗ{{вҚҺ25 3вҚ•вҚө}ВЁвҚө}frat
 gotвҶҗ8 ##.Dutils.RndF sos,sos_err,sostotal
 sosвҶҗn_effectsвҶ‘got
 sos_err sostotalвҶҗВҜ2вҶ‘got
     
 gotвҶҗ8 ##.Dutils.RndF ms,ms_err
 msвҶҗn_effectsвҶ‘got
 ms_errвҶҗВҜ1вҶ‘got
     
 titвҶҗ(вҠӮ'  Factor  '),(вҠӮ'  Sum Sq. '),(вҠӮ'     DOF  '),(вҠӮ'  Mean Sq.'),(вҠӮ'   F-ratio'),(вҠӮ'  вҚә signif.')
 equвҶҗ(вҠӮ'========  '),5вҚҙвҠӮ'  ========='
 ansвҶҗc_effects,sos,dof,ms,frat,[1.5]alfa
     
     вҚқ some like the table in a different order:  A B AB C AC BC ABC D AD ...
 :If norm вӢ„ ansвҶҗ##.Dutils.NormalTableOrder ans вӢ„ :EndIf
     
     
 errвҶҗ(вҠӮ10вҶ‘'error'),sos_err,dof_err,ms_err,(вҠӮ'  '),(вҠӮ'  ')
 totвҶҗ(вҠӮ10вҶ‘'total'),sostotal,doftotal,(вҠӮ'  '),(вҠӮ'  '),(вҠӮ'  ')
 minвҶҗ(вҠӮ'--------  '),5вҚҙвҠӮ'  --------'
 eqlвҶҗ(вҠӮ'========  '),(3вҚҙвҠӮ'  ========'),(вҠӮ'  '),(вҠӮ'  ')
     
     
 tnsвҶҗtit,[1]equ,[1]ans,[1]min,[1]err,[1]eql,[0.5]tot
     
 NS.ANOVA_TableвҶҗtns
     
     вҚқ some like the table in a different order:  A B AB C AC BC ABC D AD ...
 :If norm вӢ„ caвҶҗ##.Dutils.NormalTableOrder ca вӢ„ :EndIf
     
 nrowsвҶҗ(вүўresiduals)Г·nrep
 raveвҶҗ4 ##.Dutils.RndSВЁ(##.Dutils.SumByTwosВЁвҶ“[1]nrows nrepвҚҙresiduals)Г·nrows
     
     
     
 NS.ANOVA_AveragesвҶҗavesвҶҗ(ans[;1],ca)вҚӘ'reps'rave
 NS.ANOVA_ResidualsвҶҗresiduals
     
 ##.NS.Anova_NSвҶҗNS
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ {ns}вҶҗAnovaPool abt_mss_il_al;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;IsNumb;To;ns;abt;mss;il;al;select;list;kn;AT;head;colnames;kerr;ktop;kbot;fac;sos;cms;aph;errsos;errdof;errms;mask;ms;io;kpool;dof;newsos;newdof;newms;newesos;newedof;newems;nr;at;ker;ka;js;jd;jm;jf;ja;maskms;maskil;maskal
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   Pick up that last Anova and recalculate the Anova table
     вҚқвҲҮ    combining insignificant factors into error.
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  Examples:
     вҚқвҲҮ      AnovaPool abt {вҚ¬ вҚ¬ вҚ¬}    вҚқ pool All But The "n" biggest mean squares
     вҚқвҲҮ      AnovaPool вҚ¬ mms {вҚ¬ вҚ¬}    вҚқ pool factors with MS < Minimum Mean Square
     вҚқвҲҮ      AnovaPool вҚ¬ вҚ¬ il {вҚ¬}     вҚқ pool all Interaction Levels  il and higher
     вҚқвҲҮ      AnovaPool вҚ¬ вҚ¬ вҚ¬ al       вҚқ pool factors with an alpha вүӨ than al
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗвҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 IsNumbвҶҗ{1=2|вҺ•DRВЁвҚө}
 ToвҶҗ{(Г—вҚә-вҚө)+вҚә+(Г—вҚө-вҚә)Г—вҚі1+|вҚө-вҚә}
 nsвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
 abt mss il alвҶҗ4вҶ‘abt_mss_il_al,вҚ¬ вҚ¬ вҚ¬
 selectвҶҗвҠғвҚёabt mss il alвүўВЁвҠӮвҚ¬
     
 listвҶҗ##.NS.Anova_NS.вҺ•NL ВҜ2
 вҺ•SHADOW list
 вҚҺ(вҚ•list),'вҶҗ##.NS.Anova_NS.(',(вҚ•list),')'
     
 ATвҶҗANOVA_Table
 headвҶҗ##.Dutils.RemoveExcessBlanksВЁAT[1;]
 colnamesвҶҗ##.Dutils.RemoveExcessBlanksВЁAT[;1]
 kerrвҶҗcolnamesвҚівҠӮ'error'
 ktopвҶҗ3
 kbotвҶҗkerr-2
 maskвҶҗ(вҚівүўAT)вҲҠktop To kbot
     
 facвҶҗmask/,AT ##.Dutils.GetNamedColumns'Factor'
 sosвҶҗmask/,AT ##.Dutils.GetNamedColumns'Sum Sq.'
 dofвҶҗmask/,AT ##.Dutils.GetNamedColumns'DOF'
 cmsвҶҗmask/,AT ##.Dutils.GetNamedColumns'Mean Sq.'
 aphвҶҗmask/,AT ##.Dutils.GetNamedColumns'вҚә signif.'
     
 errsos errdof errmsвҶҗAT[kerr;2 3 4]
 :Select select
 :Case 1          вҚқ  all but n biggest MSs
     ioвҶҗвҚ’cms
     kpoolвҶҗabtвҶ“io
     
 :Case 2          вҚқ  MS < given value
     maskmsвҶҗcmsвүӨmss
     kpoolвҶҗmaskms/вҚівүўcms
     
 :Case 3          вҚқ  interaction levels:  3вүЎвүЎABC CDE .. ABCD ... ABCDE ...
     maskilвҶҗ(вүўВЁfac)вүҘil
     kpoolвҶҗmaskil/вҚівүўfac
     
 :Case 4          вҚқ  alphas < value
     maskalвҶҗaphвүҘal
     kpoolвҶҗmaskal/вҚівүўaph
     
 :Else
     'Nothing specified for Apool.  Nothing done'
     :Return
     
 :EndSelect
     
     вҚқ  pool into error and select out the resultand table
 newesosвҶҗerrsos++/sos[kpool]
 newedofвҶҗ2 ##.Dutils.RndDP errdof++/dof[kpool]
 newemsвҶҗ2 ##.Dutils.RndDP newesosГ·newedof
     
 nrвҶҗ(вҚівүўAT)~2+kpool
 atвҶҗAT[nr;]
 colnamesвҶҗcolnames[nr]
 kerвҶҗcolnamesвҚівҠӮ'error'
 at[ker;2 3 4]вҶҗnewesos newedof newems
     
     вҚқ  now recalc F and вҚә
 kaвҶҗ2вҶ“ВҜ4вҶ“(вҚівүўat)
 js jd jm jf jaвҶҗheadвҚі'Sum Sq.' 'DOF' 'Mean Sq.' 'F-ratio' 'вҚә signif.'
 at[ka;jf]вҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndDP at[ka;jm]Г·newems
 at[ka;ja]вҶҗ4 ##.Dutils.RndDP ##.Distrib.Fratio_AВЁat[ka;jf],ВЁat[ka;jd],ВЁnewedof
     
 ns.Pooled_ANOVA_TableвҶҗat
 ns.ANOVA_DataвҶҗANOVA_Data
 ns.ANOVA_ResidualsвҶҗANOVA_Residuals
 ns.ANOVA_TableвҶҗANOVA_Table
     
 ##.NS.Pooled_NSвҶҗns
 вҚҺ'##.NS.Anova_NS.Pooled_ANOVA_Table_',(selectвҠғ'NbigMS' 'LittleMS' 'FactorLevel' 'Alpha'),'вҶҗat'
 :Return
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ {ac}вҶҗAutoCorr x;y;i
     
     вҚқвҲҮ The autocorrelation of x (end held still) and y (moving forward)
     вҚқвҲҮ Gives the correlation over time of recent history
     
 yвҶҗx
 acвҶҗвҚ¬
 :For i :In ВҜ3вҶ“вҚівүўx
     
     ac,вҶҗ##.Dutils.Corr x y
     xвҶҗ1вҶ“x вӢ„ yвҶҗВҜ1вҶ“y
 :EndFor
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ {cm}вҶҗCorrel x;avex;delt;sosq;srsos;sxy;cros;names
     
     вҚқвҲҮ the correlation matrix between the input vector of vectors
     
 avexвҶҗ##.Dutils.AverageВЁx
 deltвҶҗx-avex
 sosqвҶҗ##.Dutils.SumByTwosВЁdeltГ—delt
 srsosвҶҗsosq*0.5
 sxyвҶҗ##.Dutils.SumByTwosВЁdeltвҲҳ.Г—delt
 crosвҶҗsrsosвҲҳ.Г—srsos
     
 cmвҶҗ3 ##.Dutils.RndDPВЁsxyГ·cros
     
 namesвҶҗ##.Aux.VarNamesвүўcm
     
 cmвҶҗ(' ',names),namesвҚӘcm
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ {cc}вҶҗCrossCorr(x y);i
     
     вҚқвҲҮ The autocorrelation of x (end held still) and y (moving forward)
     вҚқвҲҮ Gives the correlation over time of recent history
     
 ccвҶҗвҚ¬
 :For i :In ВҜ3вҶ“вҚівүўx
     
     cc,вҶҗ##.Dutils.Corr x y
     xвҶҗ1вҶ“x вӢ„ yвҶҗВҜ1вҶ“y
 :EndFor
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ {ns}вҶҗCrossTabs(v w);вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;uv;uw;C;c;rt;ct;gt;e;er;chq;op;tp;rp;cp;tpf;tpb;tpt;rpf;rpb;rpt;cpf;cpb
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   Do a cross-tabs or chi-square analysis: for catagorical data
     вҚқвҲҮ   It is best to have the data coded into a small (<10) number of
     вҚқвҲҮ   levels.
     вҚқвҲҮ   99 is interpreted to mean missing data.  If both are 99 the
     вҚқвҲҮ      data are eliminated.
     вҚқвҲҮ   ВҜ1 is interpreted to mean that the respondant didn't answer
     вҚқвҲҮ      the question, i.e., no response.  But obviously you can
     вҚқвҲҮ      code responses to be interpreted any way you wish.
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗвҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 nsвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
     вҚқ  remove the 99s and makes sure they are integers
 v wвҶҗвҢҠ(вҠӮ(vвү 99)вҲ§(wвү 99))/ВЁv w
     
 uv uwвҶҗ{вҚө[вҚӢвҚө]}ВЁвҲӘВЁv w     вҚқ the levels of each variable
     
     вҚқ  The counted matrix.   Levels of v are rows; levels of w are the columns
 cвҶҗ(uvвҲҳ.=v)(+.Г—)(wвҲҳ.=uw)
 rtвҶҗ+/c вӢ„ ctвҶҗ+вҢҝc вӢ„ gtвҶҗ+/rt
     
 eвҶҗ(rtвҲҳ.Г—ct)Г·gt          вҚқ what one would expect in each cell if all bets were equal
 erвҶҗc-e                  вҚқ deviation from the expected distribution
 chqвҶҗ+/,er*2             вҚқ the ChiSquare statistic
     
     вҚқ  get percentages
     
 tpfвҶҗ('overall %' '---------',uv,'---------' 'Column %'),[1.5]('  ',((вүўc)вҚҙ'|'),'  ')
 tpbвҶҗ(uwвҚӘ(вҠӮ'----')вҚӘ(0 ##.Dutils.RndDP 100Г—cГ·gt))вҚӘ(вҠӮ'----'),[0.5](0 ##.Dutils.RndDP 100Г—ctГ·gt)
 tptвҶҗ('  ',((вүўc)вҚҙ'|'),'  '),[1.5](('Row %')('-----'),(0 ##.Dutils.RndDP 100Г—rtГ·gt),'----' '100')
 tpвҶҗвҚ•tpf,tpb,tpt
     
 rpfвҶҗ('% per Row' '---------',uv),[1.5]('  ',((вүўc)вҚҙ'|'))
 rpbвҶҗ(uwвҚӘ(вҠӮ'----')вҚӘ(0 ##.Dutils.RndDP 100Г—cГ·rtвҲҳ.Г—(вҚҙct)вҚҙ1))
 rptвҶҗ('  ',((вүўc)вҚҙ'|')),[1.5](('Row %')('-----'),(0 ##.Dutils.RndDP 100Г—rtГ·gt))
 rpвҶҗвҚ•rpf,rpb,rpt
     
 cpfвҶҗ('% per Col' '---------',uv,'---------' 'Column %'),[1.5]('  ',((вүўc)вҚҙ'|'),'  ')
 cpbвҶҗ(uwвҚӘ(вҠӮ'----')вҚӘ(0 ##.Dutils.RndDP 100Г—cГ·вҶ‘(вүўc)вҚҙвҠӮct))вҚӘ(вҠӮ'----'),[0.5](0 ##.Dutils.RndDP 100Г—ctГ·gt)
 cpвҶҗвҚ•cpf,cpb
     
 ns.CT_ChiSquareвҶҗchq
 ns.CT_AlphaвҶҗ##.Distrib.ChiSq_A chq(ВҜ1+Г—/вҚҙc)
 ns.CT_Cell_CountsвҶҗc
 ns.CT_OverallPercentsвҶҗtp
 ns.CT_RowPercentsвҶҗrp
 ns.CT_ColumnPercentsвҶҗcp
     
 ##.NS.CrossTab_NSвҶҗNS
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ {NS}вҶҗFourierTransform V;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;y;ny;n;x;ay;p;ac;bc;i;s;c;a;b;m;h;g;table
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   Generate the Fourier Transform of a vector.
     вҚқвҲҮ   return the scaled frequency, real part, imaginary part, and the Power  and a table of results
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗвҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 NSвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
 yвҶҗV                             вҚқ so as to not loose the input
 nyвҶҗвүўy
 nвҶҗвҢҠ0.5Г—ny
 nвҶҗn-ny=2Г—n
 xвҶҗв—Ӣ2Г—(ВҜ1+вҚіny)Г·ny       вҚқ  scaled frequency
 ayвҶҗ##.Dutils.Average y
 yвҶҗy-ay
     
 pвҶҗacвҶҗbcвҶҗвҚ¬
     
 :For i :In вҚіn
     sвҶҗ1в—ӢiГ—x
     cвҶҗ2в—ӢiГ—x
     
     aвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwos sГ—y)Г·(##.Dutils.SumByTwos sГ—s)
     bвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwos cГ—y)Г·(##.Dutils.SumByTwos cГ—c)
     mвҶҗ(aГ—a)Г·(bГ—b)
     
     p,вҶҗm
     ac,вҶҗa
     bc,вҶҗb
     
     вҚқ      'power'##.Dutils.Watcher i m a b
 :EndFor
     
 NS.(Harmonic Real Imaginary Power)вҶҗ(вҚіn)ac bc p
     
     
 hвҶҗ(вҠӮ' harmonic'),(вҠӮ'         real    '),(вҠӮ'     imaginary   '),(вҠӮ'   power spectrum ')
 gвҶҗ(вҠӮ' ========'),(вҠӮ'  ==============='),(вҠӮ'  ==============='),(вҠӮ'  ================')
 pвҶҗ6 ##.Dutils.RndDP p
 tableвҶҗhвҚӘgвҚӘ(вҚіn),ac,bc,[1.5]p
     
 NS.TableвҶҗtable
 ##.NS.Fourier_NSвҶҗNS
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ {NS}вҶҗPrincipleComponents odata;corm;eigen;ans;data;a;d;e;z;zr;ea;tv;cv;v;n;row;b;co;r;Vup;bl;ul;nplaces;indexed_factors;ortho_factors;sorted_ortho_factors;ofactors;sofactors;tofactors;tsofactors;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;cumpct;pct;tab;factors;sfactors
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  Preform principal-component analysis on a vector of vectors.
     вҚқвҲҮ    If data ia a matrix, it must have variables as columns.
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗ1 вӢ„ вҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 NSвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
 nplacesвҶҗ3
 dataвҶҗ##.Dutils.Standardize odata
 :If 2=вүЎdata вӢ„ dataвҶҗвҶ‘[0.5]data вӢ„ :EndIf
     
 cormвҶҗ(вҚүdata)+.Г—data   вҚқ  the correlation matrix
 NS.PCOMP_CorrelationMatrixвҶҗcorm
     
 a d e zвҶҗ1 ##.Dutils.SymetricEigen corm
 NS.PCOMP_ComponentsвҶҗcomponentsвҶҗ1вҶ“z
 NS.PCOMP_EigenValuesвҶҗeigenвҶҗz[1;]
 zrвҶҗnplaces ##.Dutils.RndDPВЁz
 eaвҶҗnplaces ##.Dutils.RndDPВЁz[1;]
 tvвҶҗ+/ea
 cumpctвҶҗcvвҶҗnplaces ##.Dutils.RndDPВЁ(100Г—+\ea)Г·tv
 pctвҶҗvвҶҗnplaces ##.Dutils.RndDPВЁ100Г—eaГ·tv
 nвҶҗ2вҠғвҚҙdata
 blвҶҗnвҚҙвҠӮ' '
 ulвҶҗnвҚҙвҠӮ' ====='
 NS.PCOMP_PercentвҶҗv
 NS.PCOMP_CumulativePercentвҶҗcv
     
 tabвҶҗвҚү(вҚіn),ul,ea,bl,v,cv,bl,(вҚү1вҶ“zr)
 rowвҶҗвҶ‘20вҶ‘ВЁ(вҠӮ'  Factor no.       >'),(вҠӮ21вҚҙ'='),(вҠӮ'  Eigen Values'),(вҠӮ' '),(вҠӮ'   % Variance'),(вҠӮ'Cum. % Variance'),(вҠӮ' '),(вҠӮ'weight on var: V',вҚ•1),((вҠӮ((15вҚҙ' '),'V')),ВЁвҚ•ВЁ1вҶ“вҚіn)
 tabвҶҗвҶ‘('ВҜ'вҺ•R'-')ВЁвҶ“вҚ•row,tab
 NS.PCOMP_TableвҶҗtab
     
 bвҶҗ1вҶ“z
 NS.PCOMP_FactorsвҶҗвҶ‘('ВҜ'вҺ•R'-')ВЁвҶ“вҚ•coвҶҗdata+.Г—b
 NS.PCOMP_CovarianceMatrixвҶҗ(вҚүco)+.Г—co
 rвҶҗвүўdata
 factorsвҶҗco
 VupвҶҗ{iвҶҗвҚ’вҚө вӢ„ вҚө[i],[1.5]i}
 ortho_factorsвҶҗ4 ##.Dutils.RndDPВЁ((r-1)*0.5)Г—co
 sfactorsвҶҗVupВЁвҶ“[1]ortho_factors
     
 NS.PCOMP_OrthogonalFactorsвҶҗtofactorsвҶҗ('ВҜ'вҺ•R'-')ВЁвҚ•ВЁortho_factors
 NS.PCOMP_OrthFactorsSortedвҶҗtsofactorsвҶҗвҶ‘('ВҜ'вҺ•R'-')ВЁвҶ“(вҚ•((r,1)вҚҙвҚіr),вҠғ,/sfactors)
     
 NS.PCOMP_DiagonalвҶҗd
 NS.PCOMP_EvectorвҶҗe
 NS.PCOMP_AmatrixвҶҗa
     
      вҚқ вҲҶQL v
      вҚқ вҲҶQL cv
     
 ##.NS.Pcomp_NSвҶҗNS
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ {ns}вҶҗ{vnames}RegressChebychev(y x order);xm;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;To;io;nd;xM;cl;cheb_x;hr;sx;xsf;nsf;fp;fx;fbc;i;xhw;xc;cx;cp;cb;cy;chp;chc;cyhat;cxo;nsoc;nsoo;nsos;xtx;inv;xty;X;Y;XTX;XTY;res;cop;coyhat
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  Given:   y -- dependent (response) variable
     вҚқвҲҮ           x -- independent vector
     вҚқвҲҮ           order -- the highest power in the Cheb. polynomials
     вҚқвҲҮ           vnames -- optional names for y and x (will default to Y X)
     вҚқвҲҮ  Result:  Chebychev polynomial coefficients of the regression.
     вҚқвҲҮ           The advantage of Chebychev polynomials is that they are
     вҚқвҲҮ           independent and orthogonal AND the coefficients are
     вҚқвҲҮ           interpretable: intercept, slope, curve, cubic wiggle, etc.
     
     вҚқ because the CPs are defined on particular points on the x axis, they won't
     вҚқ match the given x's.  So, get a Forsythe ortogonal regression first (based
     вҚқ on the x's), do regressions of the forsythe polynomials to find out what
     вҚқ they are, (couldn't find any closed, recursive formula), and then get
     вҚқ Forsythe y's at the Chebychev x's.
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗвҺ•IOвҶҗ1
     
 ToвҶҗ{(Г—вҚә-вҚө)+вҚә+(Г—вҚө-вҚә)Г—вҚі1+|вҚө-вҚә}
 nsвҶҗвҺ•NS''
 :If 0=вҺ•NC'vnames' вӢ„ vnamesвҶҗ'Y' 'X' вӢ„ :EndIf
     
 ioвҶҗвҚӢx
 xвҶҗx[io]     вҚқ make sure x is monotonic
 yвҶҗy[io]
 ndвҶҗвүўy
 xMвҶҗвҢҲ/x вӢ„ xmвҶҗвҢҠ/x
 hrвҶҗ0.5Г—xM-xm     вҚқ range
 clвҶҗ0.5Г—xM+xm     вҚқ center
     
 cheb_xвҶҗ##.Dutils.MakeChebychevPolynomialX 0 nd
 hrГ·вҶҗВҜ1вҶ‘cheb_x
 sxвҶҗ(cl,1)Г·hr
 xsfвҶҗ(x-cl)Г·hr
     
 nsfвҶҗvnames ##.Stats.RegressForsythe(y x order)
 fpвҶҗnsf.ForsythePolynomialsOnX
 fxвҶҗfp[;2]
 fbcвҶҗ,вҠӮ(0 1)             вҚқ  "x" is centered.
      вҚқ  get regressions for fp[;i]
 :For i :In 3 To order+1
     :Trap 0
         fbc,вҶҗвҠӮzвҶҗfp[;i]вҢ№fxвҲҳ.*ВҜ1+вҚіi
     :Else
         XвҶҗfxвҲҳ.*ВҜ1+вҚіi вӢ„ YвҶҗfp[;i]
         XTXвҶҗ(вҚүX)+.Г—X вӢ„ XTYвҶҗY+.Г—X
         res diglвҶҗ2вҶ‘XTY ##.Dutils.SolveSLAE XTX
         fbc,вҶҗвҠӮres
     :EndTrap
 :EndFor
     вҚқ Scale the cheb_x locations to span fx:  cheb_x spans ВҜ1 to 1
 xMвҶҗвҢҲ/fx вӢ„ xmвҶҗвҢҠ/fx
 xhwвҶҗ0.5Г—xM-xm     вҚқ range
 xcвҶҗ0.5Г—xM+xm     вҚқ center
     
 cxвҶҗxc+xhwГ—cheb_x
     
     вҚқ Use the fbs to get cp
 cpвҶҗ1,[1.5]cx
 :For i :In 2 To order
     cp,вҶҗ(cxвҲҳ.*0,вҚіi)+.Г—iвҠғfbc
 :EndFor
     
     вҚқ Use the fbs to get cp
 fbвҶҗ1,[1.5]fx
 :For i :In 2 To order
     fb,вҶҗ(fxвҲҳ.*0,вҚіi)+.Г—iвҠғfbc
 :EndFor
     
 cyвҶҗcp+.Г—nsf.Coefficients
     вҚқ  we now have an x and y to use:  cheb_x and cy
     вҚқ  make the Chebychev Polynmomials
 chpвҶҗ##.Dutils.MakeChebychevPolys cheb_x order
 chcвҶҗcyвҢ№chp
 cyhatвҶҗchp+.Г—chc
 copвҶҗ##.Dutils.MakeChebychevPolys fx order
 coyhatвҶҗcop+.Г—chc
 cxoвҶҗcx+xhw+вҠғx    вҚқ  this corresponds to x
 xtxвҶҗ+вҢҝchp*2
 xtyвҶҗcy+.Г—cxo
 invвҶҗГ·{вҚө+0.000001000001Г—вҚө=0}xtx
     
     
     вҚқ  The plots of x:y x:Yhat and cxo:cyhat  should make sense
     вҚқ 'a3'вҲҶPADD'FP'(4.28 30)
     вҚқ 'a3'вҲҶQP x y
     вҚқ 'a3'вҲҶQP x nsf.Yhat
     вҚқ 'a3'вҲҶQP cxo cyhat
     вҚқ 'a3'вҲҶQT'X' 'y Yhat cyhat' 'Check on Forsythe and Cehbychev Regressions'
     
 ns.CYhatвҶҗcyhat
 ns.COYhatвҶҗnsf.Yhat
 ns.CoefficientsвҶҗchc
 ns.ChebychevPolyNomialsвҶҗchp
 ns.YвҶҗy
 ns.XвҶҗx
 ns.CXвҶҗcxo
 ns.CYвҶҗcy
 ns.CResidualsвҶҗcy-cyhat
 ns.COResidualsвҶҗnsf.Residuals
 ns.DLвҶҗ0
     
     вҚқ  Statistics need to come from the Forsythe regression.
     вҚқ  The Chebylchev regression just copies the Forsythe.
     
 ns.(AnovaTable Results ResidualsTable Statistics DL Yhat Residuals)вҶҗnsf.(AnovaTable Results ResidualsTable Statistics DL Yhat Residuals)
 ##.NS.Chebychev_NSвҶҗns
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ {ns}вҶҗ{vnames}RegressForsythe(y x order);вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;n;nb;one;i;ib;xbar;fp;co;xtx;xty;b;ybar;xto;aone;dl;nsoc;inv;yhat;nsoo;nsos;in;tr;bp;bod
     
     вҚқвҲҮ do an orthjogonal Forsythe Polynomial Regression      #.MOST.FORSY
                                                  вҚқ #.MOST.MOSTвҲҶMвҲҶFORS_REGR
 вҺ•MLвҶҗвҺ•IOвҶҗ1                                   вҚқ #.MOST.MOSTвҲҶMвҲҶFORSYTHE вүЎ ##.Dutils.ForsytheX
 nsвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
 nвҶҗвүўy
 :If 0=вҺ•NC'vnames' вӢ„ vnamesвҶҗ'Y' 'Const',('X',ВЁвҚ•ВЁвҚіВҜ1+вүўx) вӢ„ :EndIf
     
 nbвҶҗorder+1
 oneвҶҗnвҚҙ1
     
 iвҶҗn nвҚҙ1,nвҚҙ0
 ibвҶҗnb nbвҚҙ1,nbвҚҙ0
     
 xbarвҶҗ##.Dutils.Average x
 fp coвҶҗ##.Dutils.MakeForsythePolys x order
 xtxвҶҗ+вҢҝfp*2             вҚқ  all off diagonal elements are 0 except for round-off
 xtyвҶҗy+.Г—fp
 bвҶҗxtyГ·xtx              вҚқ  therefore, don't need  вҢ№
 yhatвҶҗfp+.Г—b
 ybarвҶҗвҠғb
 xtoвҶҗone+.Г—fp
 aoneвҶҗxtoГ·xtx
 invвҶҗГ·{вҚө+0.000001000001Г—вҚө=0}xtx
     
 dlвҶҗ0
 :Trap 0
     inвҶҗвҢ№(вҚүfp)+.Г—fp
     trвҶҗ1 1вҚүin
     bpвҶҗвҢҲ/|tr
     inГ·вҶҗbp
     (1 1вҚүin)вҶҗ0
     bodвҶҗвҢҲ/,|in
     dlвҶҗ2 ##.Dutils.RndDP 0вҢҲ17+10вҚҹ|bod
 :EndTrap
     
 nsocвҶҗ##.Dutils.OrthoCalc(x y fp b xty xtx inv xbar ybar vnames)
 nsooвҶҗ##.Dutils.OrthoOut nsoc
 nsosвҶҗ##.Dutils.OrthoStats nsoc
     
