вҲҮ {NS}вҶҗ{vnames}RegressMultipleLinear(y x);вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;nd;X;ybar;xbar;nv;c;idof;cdof;tdof;edof;rdof;I;Ib;dl;as;a;CN;XTY;XTX;Yhat;ai;check;ns;nsc;nsr;nss;coeffs
     
     вҚқвҲҮ Given:   y -- the response variable
     вҚқвҲҮ          x -- a nested vector of independent x variables
     вҚқвҲҮ               N.B. if the first x is a vector of 1s, its
     вҚқвҲҮ               coefficient is the "intercept".
     вҚқвҲҮ               If not the solution is "forced thru the origin".
     вҚқвҲҮ          vnames:  optional names for the y and x variables
     вҚқвҲҮ             e.g.:  'ProductQuality' 'Volume' 'Time' 'Weight' 'Conc_1'  'Conc_2'
     вҚқвҲҮ Result:  the coefficients of the regression
     вҚқвҲҮ          other results are saved in the namespace:  Regress_NS
     вҚқвҲҮ          this will include:  Anova for the analysis, various
     вҚқвҲҮ          statistics, predictions, residuals, etc.
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗвҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 NSвҶҗвҺ•NS''
 :If 0=вҺ•NC'vnames' вӢ„ vnamesвҶҗ'Y' 'Const',('X',ВЁвҚ•ВЁвҚіВҜ1+вүўx) вӢ„ :EndIf
     
 ndвҶҗвүўy
 XвҶҗвҶ‘[0.5]x
 ybarвҶҗ##.Dutils.Average y
 xbarвҶҗвҠғВЁ##.Dutils.AverageВЁx
 nvвҶҗвүўx
     
     вҚқ  although  cвҶҗyвҢ№X  does the job - because regression is particularly
     вҚқ  susseptible to degenerate cases (correlated x's), I prefer
     вҚқ  to solve the equations myself and monitor the pivots to estimate
     вҚқ  singularity (matrix condition).
     
 :Trap 0
     NS.C_aplвҶҗcвҶҗyвҢ№вҶ‘[0.5]x
 :EndTrap
     
     вҚқ  is the first variable a vector of 1s
 idofвҶҗвҲ§/1=вҠғx
 cdofвҶҗnv-idof
 tdofвҶҗnd
 edofвҶҗtdof-nv
 rdofвҶҗnd-idof
     
 IвҶҗnd ndвҚҙ1,ndвҚҙ0
 IbвҶҗnv nvвҚҙ1,nvвҚҙ0
     
 XTXвҶҗ(вҚүX)+.Г—X
 XTYвҶҗ(вҚүX)+.Г—y
     
 coeffs dl ai a check CNвҶҗXTY ##.Dutils.SolveSLAE XTX
     
 NS.CoeffsвҶҗcoeffs
 NS.ConditionNumberвҶҗCN
 NS.DigitsLostвҶҗdl
     
     
 NS.YвҶҗy
 NS.XвҶҗX
 NS.YhatвҶҗYhatвҶҗX+.Г—coeffs
 NS.ResidualsвҶҗy-Yhat
     
     
 nscвҶҗ##.Dutils.RegressCalc X y coeffs XTY ai xbar ybar Ib vnames
 nsrвҶҗ##.Dutils.RegressResults nsc
 nssвҶҗdl ##.Dutils.RegressStats nsc
     
 NS.(Result AnovaR)вҶҗnsr.(Result AnovaR)
 NS.(Stats ResidTable)вҶҗnss.(Stats ResidTable)
     
 ##.NS.Regress_NSвҶҗNS
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ {ns}вҶҗ{vnames}RegressPolynomial(y x order);вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;nd;nv;xbar;ybar;X;idof;cdof;tdof;edof;rdof;I;Ib;XTX;XTY;coeffs;dl;ai;a;check;CN;Yhat;nsc;nsr;nss
     
     вҚқвҲҮ do a regular yвҶҗa+bx+cx^2+dx^3... regression
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗвҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 nsвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
 ndвҶҗвүўy
 nvвҶҗorder+1
     
 :If 0=вҺ•NC'vnames' вӢ„ vnamesвҶҗ'Y' 'Const',('X',ВЁвҚ•ВЁвҚіnv-1) вӢ„ :EndIf
     
 xbarвҶҗ##.Dutils.Average x
 ybarвҶҗ##.Dutils.Average y
     
 XвҶҗxвҲҳ.*0,вҚіorder
     
      вҚқ   the first variable is a vector of 1s
 idofвҶҗ1
 cdofвҶҗnv-idof
 tdofвҶҗnd
 edofвҶҗtdof-nv
 rdofвҶҗnd-idof
     
 IвҶҗnd ndвҚҙ1,ndвҚҙ0
 IbвҶҗnv nvвҚҙ1,nvвҚҙ0
     
 XTXвҶҗ(вҚүX)+.Г—X
 XTYвҶҗ(вҚүX)+.Г—y
     
 coeffs dl ai a check CNвҶҗXTY ##.Dutils.SolveSLAE XTX
     
 ns.CoeffsвҶҗcoeffs
 ns.ConditionNumberвҶҗCN
 ns.DigitsLostвҶҗdl
     
     
 ns.YвҶҗy
 ns.XвҶҗX
 ns.YhatвҶҗYhatвҶҗX+.Г—coeffs
 ns.ResidualsвҶҗy-Yhat
     
     
 nscвҶҗ##.Dutils.RegressCalc X y coeffs XTY XTX ai xbar ybar Ib vnames
 nsrвҶҗ##.Dutils.RegressResults nsc
 nssвҶҗdl ##.Dutils.RegressStats nsc
     
 ns.(Result AnovaR)вҶҗnsr.(Result AnovaR)
 ns.(Stats ResidTable)вҶҗnss.(Stats ResidTable)
     
 ##.NS.Polynomial_NSвҶҗns
     
 :Return
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ (xans dl)вҶҗSimutaneousEquations(A R);ai;a;check;CN
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   Solve a set of simultaneous eqns:
     вҚқвҲҮ        aw + bx + cy + dz = r1        a b c d
     вҚқвҲҮ        ew + fx + gy + hz = r2   A вүЎвүЎ e f g h   R вүЎвүЎ r1 r2 r3 r4  Ans вүЎвүЎ w x y z
     вҚқвҲҮ        iw + jx + ky + lz = r3        i j k l
     вҚқвҲҮ        mw + nx + oy + pz = r4        m n o p
     
     
 xans dl ai a check CNвҶҗR ##.Dutils.SolveSLAE A
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

