вҲҮ Example_Pcomps;factors
     
 ##.Stuff.pdataвҶҗ##.Stuff.MakePData
 nspвҶҗ##.Stats.Pcomps #.Stuff.pdata
 factorsвҶҗnsp.PCOMP_Factors
 'fac'вҲҶQL 1вҶ“(вҚівүўfactors),6вҶ‘[2]factors
     
 :Return
