вҲҮ {ns}вҶҗFourier y;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;N;n;x;ay;p;i;s;c;a;b;m;rp;ip;h;d;ftable
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   compute the Fourier transform of a variable
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗвҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 nsвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
 NвҶҗвүўy
 nвҶҗ{вҚө{вҚө-вҚә=вҚөГ—2}вҢҠвҚөГ·2}N
 xвҶҗв—Ӣ2Г—(ВҜ1+вҚіN)Г·N
 ayвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwos y)Г·N
 yвҶҗy-ay
 pвҶҗrpвҶҗipвҶҗвҚ¬
     
 :For i :In вҚіN
     s cвҶҗ{1 2в—ӢвҠӮвҚө}iГ—x
     aвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwos sГ—y)+(##.Dutils.SumByTwos sГ—s)
     bвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwos cГ—y)+(##.Dutils.SumByTwos cГ—c)
     mвҶҗвҠғ+/a b*2
     p,вҶҗm
     rp,вҶҗa
     ip,вҶҗb
 :EndFor
     
 hвҶҗ(вҠӮ' harmonic'),(вҠӮ'         real    '),(вҠӮ'     imaginary   '),(вҠӮ'       power     ')
 dвҶҗ(вҠӮ' ========'),(вҠӮ'  ==============='),(вҠӮ'  ==============='),(вҠӮ'  ===============')
 ftableвҶҗhвҚӘdвҚӘ(вҚіN),rp,ip,[1.5]p
     
 ns.FOURIER_PowerSpectrumвҶҗp
 ns.FOURIER_RealPartPowerSpectrumвҶҗrp
 ns.FOURIER_ImaginaryPartPowerSpectrumвҶҗip
 ns.FOURIER_TableвҶҗftable
     
 'ps'#.grf.вҲҶQP ВҜ1вҶ“p
 'ps'#.grf.вҲҶQT'harmonic number or scaled frequency' 'Power' 'Power Spectrum'
     
 ##.NS.Fourier_NSвҶҗns
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ {ns}вҶҗFourier_po2 y;вҺ•ML;вҺ•IO;n;x;ay;p;i;s;c;a;b;m;rp;ip;h;d;ftable
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   compute the Fourier transform of a variable  having a power of 2 points
     
 вҺ•MLвҶҗвҺ•IOвҶҗ1
 nsвҶҗвҺ•NS''
     
 nвҶҗвүўy
 nвҶҗ2*вҢҠ2вҚҹn
 yвҶҗnвҶ‘y
 xвҶҗв—Ӣ2Г—(ВҜ1+вҚіn)Г·n
 ayвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwos y)Г·n
 y-y-ay
 pвҶҗrpвҶҗipвҶҗвҚ¬
     
 :For i :In вҚіn
     s cвҶҗ{1 2в—ӢвҠӮвҚө}iГ—x
     aвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwos sГ—y)+(##.Dutils.SumByTwos sГ—s)
     bвҶҗ(##.Dutils.SumByTwos cГ—y)+(##.Dutils.SumByTwos cГ—c)
     mвҶҗвҠғ+/a b*2
     p,вҶҗm
     rp,вҶҗa
     ip,вҶҗb
 :EndFor
     
 hвҶҗ(вҠӮ' harmonic'),(вҠӮ'         real    '),(вҠӮ'     imaginary   '),(вҠӮ'       power     ')
 dвҶҗ(вҠӮ' ========'),(вҠӮ'  ==============='),(вҠӮ'  ==============='),(вҠӮ'  ===============')
 ftableвҶҗhвҚӘdвҚӘ(вҚіn),rp,ip,[1.5]p
     
 ns.FOURIER_PowerSpectrumвҶҗp
 ns.FOURIER_RealPartPowerSpectrumвҶҗrp
 ns.FOURIER_ImaginaryPartPowerSpectrumвҶҗip
 ns.FOURIER_TableвҶҗftable
     
 'ps'#.grf.вҲҶQP ВҜ1вҶ“p
 'ps'#.grf.вҲҶQT'harmonic number or scaled frequency' 'Power' 'Power Spectrum'
     
 ##.NS.Fourier_NSвҶҗns
     
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ fвҶҗGamma_pdf(x k t)
     
     вҚқвҲҮ  f(x) based on k (shape) and theta (scale)  :: or alphaвүЎshape : beta=rate (Г·theta)<>spread
     вҚқвҲҮ  f(x;k,t)вҶҗ(1 + Gamma(k) Г— t*k)   Г—   (x*k-1)   Г—   (*-xГ·t)
     вҚқвҲҮ  f(x;a,b)вҶҗ((b*a)Г·Gamma(a))  Г—  (x*a-1)  Г— (*-bГ—x)
     
     
     вҚқвҲҮ   baby gamma(a,bx) is the lower incomplete gamma function
     вҚқвҲҮ   big  Gamma(a) is the gamma function (generalized
     вҚқвҲҮ   GAMMA(a,b) is the gamma distribution
     
     
     
     вҚқвҲҮ      f(x;a,b)=  (b*a)(x*a-1)(e*-bx) / Gammma(a)
     
     вҚқвҲҮ      F(x;a,b)=  gamma(a,bx)/Gamma(a)                                                                 вҚқвҲҮ
     вҚқвҲҮ      F(x;a,b)=  interal[0 x] of f(u;a,b)du
     вҚқвҲҮ      F(x;a,b)=  1 - +/((bx)*i)(*-bx) Г· !i   = (*-bx) Г— +/((bx)*1) Г· !i
     
     вҚқвҲҮ     -вҚҹU  is distributed  GAMMA(1,1)
вҲҮ

вҲҮ XвҶҗd GetChi a
 i+вҶҗ1
     вҚқ 'Chisq_i_a_d'##.Dutils.Watcher i a d
 XвҶҗ##.Distrib.ChiSq_Xa a d
