вҲҮ FвҶҗalpha GetFratio(dod don)
     
 i+вҶҗ1
 'Fratio_i_a_n_d'##.Dutils.Watcher i alpha don dod
     вҚқ FвҶҗ##.Distrib.Fratio_F alpha don dod
 FвҶҗ##.Distrib.Fratio_Fa alpha don dod
 :Return
вҲҮ

вҲҮ tвҶҗd GetT a
